\id MRK
\h Markus
\toc1 Markus
\toc2 Markus
\toc3 Mk.
\mt1 Markus
\c 1
\s1 Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ d cchadet nnes x Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 1 Beddu n L’Injil n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, Mmis n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt [Mt. 3:1-17; 4:1-11; Lk. 3:1-9; 15-17; 21-22; 4:-13; Yḥ. 1:19-28] \x*
\v 2 Am mammec tura deg \add wedlis n\add* unabi Icaɛya ...
\b
\m \qt “Aqa Necc ad ssekkeɣ\qt*
\m \qt zzat i wudem nnec lmalak inu,\qt*
\m \qt wenni i ɣa isswejden abrid nnec.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Uf. 23:20; Mal. 3:1; Mt. 11:10; Lk. 7:27. \x*
\m 
\v 3 \qt “Tmijja \tl n wenni\tl* isɣuyyun di řexřa:\qt*
\m \qt ‘Swejdem abrid n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt seggmem imesraq nnes!’”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Ica. 40:3; Mt. 3:3; Lk. 3:4; Yḥ. 1:23. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 4 ... \add ammu i\add* tuɣa Yuḥanna isseɣḍaṣ di řexřa, ittbarreḥ s useɣḍeṣ n ttubet i weɣfar n ddnub. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Mt. 3:1; Lk. 3:3; Yḥ. 3:23. \x*
\v 5 Ffɣen-dd ɣares marra jjwayeh n Yahudiyya d ayt n Urcalim, ttwassɣeḍṣen zzayes deg iɣzar n L’Urdun am neɛɛmen s ddnub nsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Mt. 3:5; Lk. 3:7. \x*
\m 
\v 6 Tuɣa Yuḥanna wanita yarḍ taḍuft n iřeɣman, ibekkes s yijj n webyas n yiřem x tejɛinna nnes, u tuɣa ittett iburexsen d tamment taḥurrect. \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Ij. 1:8; Lawi 11:22; Mt. 3:4. \x*
\v 7 Tuɣa ittbarreḥ, iqqar: “Xzar, ad dd-yas awarni ayi wenni ijehden xafi, wenni umi war sdihiǧeɣ ad aḍareɣ maḥend ad fesyeɣ ifiřan n sandaliyat nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Mt. 3:11; Lk. 3:16; Yḥ. 1:27. \x*
\v 8 Necc ssɣeḍṣeɣ kenniw deg waman, maca Netta ad kenniw isseɣḍeṣ di Arruḥ Iqeddsen.” \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Ica. 44:3; Yuw. 3:1; Mt. 3:11; Řex. 1:5; 2:4; 11:15, 16; 19:4. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 Deg wussan nni yusa-dd Yasuɛ zi Nnaṣira, di Ljalil, ittwasseɣḍeṣ zi Yuḥanna deg yeɣzar n L’Urdun. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt [Mt. 3:13-17; Lk. 3:21-22] \x*
\v 10 Deɣya, am dd-igeɛɛed zeg waman, iẓra ijenwan arzmen uca Arruḥ am tedbirt tehwa-dd xas. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Mt. 3:16; Lk. 3:21; Yḥ. 1:32. \x*
\v 11 Tusa-dd ict n tmijja zeg ijenwan: \bd “Cek d Mmi iɛizzen, dayek ufiɣ arḍa inu.”\bd*\x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Izhd. 2:7; Ica. 5:1; 42:1; Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 9:7; Lk. 3:22; 9:35; Ɛbr. 1:5; 5:5; Kul. 1:13; 2 Bṭ. 1:17. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 Deɣya igewwed i-t Arruḥ ɣar řexřa. \x ◘ \xo 1:12 \xt [Mt. 4:1-11; Lk. 4:1-13] — Mt. 4:1; Lk. 4:1. \x*
\v 13 Uca \bd iqqim din di řexřa arebɛin n wussan\bd*, ijarreb i-t cciṭan, tuɣa-t ak-d řewḥuc uca sexxarent xas lmalakat.
\b
\s1 Tařaɣit n Yasuɛ x imeḥḍaren imezwura
\m 
\v 14 Awarni řami ṭṭfen Yuḥanna, yudef-dd Yasuɛ ɣar Ljalil, ittbarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Tgeldit, \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt [Mt. 4:12-22; Lk. 4:14-15; 5:1-11] — Mt. 4:12; Mk. 6:17, 18; Lk. 4:14; Yḥ. 4:43. \x*
\v 15 inna: “Aqa řweqt tiweḍ-dd, tqarreb-dd Tgeldit n AREBBI. Tubem, amnem di Řexbar Aṣebḥan.”
\b
\m 
\v 16 Am tuɣa iggur ɣar řebḥar n Ljalil, iẓra Cimɛun d Andrawus umas, neṭṭaren tracca di řebḥar, maɣar nitni d ineymaren n iseřman. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Mt. 4:18. \x*
\v 17 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Asem-dd awarni ayi uca ad kenniw arreɣ d ineymaren n yewdan.” \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Irm. 16:16; Ḥiz. 47:10. \x*
\v 18 Řexdenni jjin tiracciwin nsen uca ḍfaren t. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Mt. 19:27; Mk. 10:28; Lk. 5:11; 18:28. \x*
\v 19 Xenni awarni řami iɛdu cwayt ssenni, iẓra Yaɛqub mmis n Zabdi d umas Yuḥanna di tɣarrabut, ɛedřen tiracciwin nsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt Mt. 4:21. \x*
\v 20 Iřaɣa xasen uca řexdenni jjin babatsen Zabdi ak-d ixemmasen di tɣarrabut, uca ḍfaren t.
\b
\s1 Ameryaḥ di temzida n Kafernaḥum
\m 
\v 21 Xeccen ɣar Kafarnaḥum uca deɣya \add ibda\add* isseřmad di ssebt di temzida. \x ◘ \xo 1:21 \xt [Lk. 4:31-37] — Mt. 4:13; Lk. 4:31. \x*
\v 22 Tbehten zeg useřmed nnes, minzi isseřmed i-ten am wenni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa, war iǧi am yimseřmaden n idlisen. \x ◘ \xo 1:22 \xt Mt. 7:28; Lk. 4:32. \x*
\v 23 Tuɣa di temzida nsen ijj n bnadem dayes ijj n řaryaḥ d amengus, isɣuyyu, \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Lk. 4:33. \x*
\v 24 iqqar: “Min din jar aneɣ neccin d Cek a Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri. Ma tusid-dd ḥima ad aneɣ tesshellked? Aqa necc ssneɣ Cek min teɛnid: \add Aqa Cek\add* d Amqeddas n AREBBI.”
\v 25 Uca iɛřem as Yasuɛ, inna as: “Sqar! Ffeɣ zzayes!”
\v 26 Immenḍar i-t řaryaḥ amengus, isɣuy s ict n tɣuyyit tejhed uca xenni iffeɣ-dd zzayes.
\v 27 Tbehten marra, mmseqsan ak-d wayawya, nnan: “Man aya? Mana taɣuri-ya n jdid? Minzi s ṣṣulṭa yumur uřa d řaryaḥ imengas uca tteggen as array.”
\v 28 Řexdenni iffeɣ řexbar nnes ɣar marra jjwayeh i d as dd-innḍen i Ljalil.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n tḍekkwač n Buṭrus s ufus n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 29 \add Awarni řami\add* dd-ffɣen zi temzida, ruḥen ɣar taddart n Cimɛun d Andrawus ak-d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna. \x ◘ \xo 1:29 \xt [Mt. 8:14-17; Lk. 4:38-41] — Mt. 8:14; Lk. 4:38. \x*
\v 30 Tuɣa taḍekkwač n Cimɛun tezzeř s tmessi, uca nitni ssiwřen xas akides.
\v 31 Iqarreb-dd ɣares, icebbar deg ufus nnes, issgeɛɛed i-tt-i-dd. Deɣya tejja xas tmessi uca nettat \add tebda\add* tᵉttsexxar xasen.
\v 32 Řami dd-tiweḍ tmeddit, tafuct truḥ ad teɣři, iwyen ɣares marra imehřac d inni daysen ccwaṭen. \x ◘ \xo 1:32 \xt Mt. 8:16; Lk. 4:40. \x*
\v 33 Tuɣa tandint marra tmun ɣar tewwart.
\v 34 Issgenfa aṭṭas n imeḥřac s ɛřam kuř řehřacat uca issuffeɣ aṭṭas n ccwaṭen, war ijji ccwaṭen ad ssiwřen, minzi ssnen t.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ iẓẓuǧ ɣar ṣṣbeḥ zic
\m 
\v 35 Tiwecca zic, \add tuɣa ɛad d ǧiřet,\add* ikkar uca iffeɣ ɣar ijj n wemcan ixřan, tuɣa ittẓaǧa din. \x ◘ \xo 1:35 \xt [Lk. 4:42-44] — Mt. 14:23; Lk. 4:42. \x*
\v 36 Cimɛun d yinni tuɣa akides, arzun xas.
\v 37 Řami t ufin, nnan as: “Marra iwdan arezzun xak!”
\v 38 Inna asen: “Ittxeṣṣa ad nraḥ ɣar dcurat d tneddam yudsen, ḥima ad din barrḥeɣ ɛawed minzi aqa i uya umi dd-usiɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 1:38 \xt Ica. 61:1; Lk. 4:18, 43. \x*
\v 39 Tuɣa isseřmad di temzidawin nsen di marra Ljalil, u issuffuɣ ccwaṭen.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n bnadem dayes řbarṣ
\m 
\v 40 Yusa-dd ɣares ijjen dayes řbarṣ, iwḍa ɣar iḍaren nnes, ittar as, inna: “Mařa texsed, tzemmared ad ayi tessizdeged.” \x ◘ \xo 1:40 \xt [Mt. 8:1-4; Lk. 5:12-16] — Mt. 8:2; Lk. 5:12. \x*
\v 41 Izziǧez i Yasuɛ, isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes, iḥada i-t, inna as: “Xseɣ! Iwa, dweř d amezdag!”
\v 42 Di tsaɛɛet nni, řexdenni iruḥ xas řbarṣ uca idweř izdig.
\v 43 Uca \add awarni řami\add* d as iɛřem, issekk i-t řexdenni,
\v 44 inna as: “Xzar, war t ttɛiwid uřa i yijjen, maca ruḥ, scen ixef nnec i ukehhan uca ewc x usizdeg nnec min yumur Musa maḥend ad tcehded i nitni.” \x ◘ \xo 1:44 \xt Lawi 13:2; 14:1. \x*
\v 45 Maca řami iruḥ, ibda ittbarreḥ aṭṭas, issuffeɣ řexbar ařami war izemmar Yasuɛ ad yadef ɣar tandint s bṭayṭay, maca tuɣa-t barra deg imucan ixřan, tuɣa ttasen-dd ɣares zi kuř jjwayeh.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n uneɛḍab
\m 
\v 1 Awarni i ca n wussan Yudef Yasuɛ ɛawed ɣar Kafarnaḥum. Řami sřin belli aqa-t di taddart, \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt [Mt. 9:1-8; Lk. 5:17-26] — Mt. 9:1; Lk. 5:17. \x*
\v 2 munen xas waṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*, ařami war zemmaren ad dd-awḍen uřa ɣar tewwart, u Netta tuɣa issawař akidsen s Wawař.
\v 3 Usin-dd ca ɣares, iwyen-dd ijj n uneɛḍab ɣares, arbun t-i-dd jar asen arebɛa n yeryazen. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Mt. 9:1; Lk. 5:18. \x*
\v 4 Minzi war zemmaren ad ɣares dd-qarrben zi ssibbet n řɣaci, gaɛɛden x tzeqqa, ksin cwayt zi tzeqqa sennej amcan mani tuɣa Yasuɛ, uca ssehwan-dd tassut min xef izzeř uneɛḍab.
\m 
\v 5 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ l’iman nsen, inna i uneɛḍab: “\add A\add* mmi, aqa ddnub nnec ttwaɣfaren.”
\v 6 Tuɣa qqimen din ca n imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen, ttxarraṣen deg wuř nsen:
\v 7 “Min iɛna wa i ittceqqafen \add ammu\add*? Wi izemmaren ad iɣfar ddnub mɣir AREBBI weḥḥdes?” \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Izhd. 32:5; 51:3; Ica. 43:25. \x*
\v 8 Yuca Yasuɛ s Arruḥ nnes belli aqa ttxarraṣen ammu deg ixef nsen. Inna asen: “Mayemmi tᵉttxemmamem di man aya deg wuřawen nwem?
\v 9 Min ihewnen ad iniɣ i uneɛḍab: ‘Ttwaɣfaren ddnub nnec’ niɣ ad iniɣ: ‘Kkar, ksi tassut nnec uca uyur’?
\v 10 Maca ḥima ad tessnem belli Mmis n bnadem ɣares ṣṣulṭa x temmurt, maḥend ad iɣfar ddnub, inna xenni i uneɛḍab:
\v 11 ‘Necc ad ac iniɣ: Kkar, ksi tassut nnec, truḥed ɣar taddart nnec!’”
\v 12 Deɣya ikkar, řexdenni iksi tassut nnes uca iffeɣ qibač i marra \add iwdan\add*, ařami tbehten marra, ssemɣaren di AREBBI, nnan: “Ɛemmarṣ war neẓri man aya!”
\b
\s1 Tařaɣit n Yasuɛ x Matta Lawi
\m 
\v 13 Xenni iffeɣ ɛawed ɣar řebḥar, uca yusa-dd ɣares řɣaci marra uca isseřmed i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt [Mt. 9:9-13; Lk. 5:27-32] — Mt. 9:9; Lk. 5:27. \x*
\v 14 Am yeɛdu, ibarq Lawi mmis n Ḥalfa iqqim ɣar taddart n ḍḍariba, uca inna as: “Ḍfar ayi-dd!”. Ikkar uca iḍfar i-t.
\v 15 Am iqqim Netta \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* di taddart nnes, tuɣa aṭṭas n ayt n ḍḍariba d imednab qqimen ak-d Yasuɛ d imeḥḍaren nnes, minzi tuɣa aten deg waṭṭas uca ḍfaren t.
\v 16 Umi ẓrin imseřmaden n idlisen d Ifarisiyyen aqa ittett ak-d ayt n ḍḍariba d imednab, nnan i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Mayemmi ittett, isess ak-d ayt n ḍḍariba d imednab?”
\v 17 Řami isřa Yasuɛ man aya, inna asen: “Inni iṣeḥḥen war ḥdijen ca aḍbib, maca imehřac wah. Aqa war dd-usiɣ ḥima ad řaɣiɣ i yinni iseggden maca i imednab.” \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Mt. 9:13; 21:31; Lk. 5:32; 19:10; 1 Tim. 1:15. \x*
\b
\s1 Aseqsi x uẓummi
\m 
\v 18 Tuɣa imeḥḍaren n Yuḥanna \add Amseɣḍaṣ\add* d Ifarisiyyen ttẓumman uca \add xenni\add* usin-dd ɣares, nnan as: “Mayemmi ttẓumman imeḥḍaren n Yuḥanna d Ifarisiyyen, \add maca\add* imeḥḍaren nnec war ttẓummin ca?” \x ◘ \xo 2:18 \xt [Mt. 9:14-17; Lk. 5:33-39] — Mt. 9:14; Lk. 5:33. \x*
\v 19 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Ma zemmaren tarwa n umuřay ad ẓummen d umuřay \add ɛad\add* akidsen? Lla!\x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Ica. 62:5; 2 Kur. 11:2. \x*
\v 20 Maca ad dd-asen wussan xmi d ɣa immeksi umuřay xasen, xenni ad ẓummen, deg wussan nni.
\v 21 War iǧi ḥed ittxeyyeḍ taneqqič zi tcuqqet n jdid x warruḍ aqdim, niɣ xenni taneqqič nni n jdid ad teqřeɛ zeg \add warruḍ\add* abuřay, uca ad idweř ucarreg imɣar.
\v 22 Uřa d ijj war ittfarreɣ binu n jdid di txuncay tiqdimin, ḥima binu n jdid war ittcarrig tixuncay u tixuncay ad ḍeyyɛent uca binu ad izeǧeɛ. Maca ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaffareɣ binu n jdid di txuncay n jdid.” \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Mt. 9:17. \x*
\b
\s1 Mmis n bnadem d Bab n ssebt
\m 
\v 23 Xenni imsar aqa icuq Yasuɛ deg iyyaren n imendi di ssebt, uca imeḥḍaren nnes bdan řeqqḍen tidrin am gguren. \x ◘ \xo 2:23 \xt [Mt. 12:1-8; Lk. 6:1-5] — Aɛwd. 23:24; Mt. 12:1; Lk. 6:1. \x*
\v 24 Nnan as Ifarisiyyen: “Xzar, mayemmi tteggen di ssebt min war iḥeǧřen?” \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Uf. 20:10; Aɛwd. 23:25\x*
\v 25 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Ma war teɣrim qaɛ min igga Dawud, řami tuɣa ittwaḥṣar, iṭṭef i-t řaẓ, netta d yinni akides? \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt Lawi 24:8; 1 Ṣm. 21:6. \x*
\v 26 Mammec dd-yudef ɣar Taddart n AREBBI deg wussan n Abyatar, arrays n ikehhanen, uca icca aɣrum n wescan n SIDI i war iḥeǧřen ad t ccen mɣir ikehhanen waha, uca iwca ɛawed i yinni tuɣa akides?” \x ◘ \xo 2:26 \xt Lawi 24:9. \x*
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* inna asen: “Aqa ass n ssebt ittwagg i bnadem, war iǧi bnadem i ssebt.
\v 28 Ammu i iǧa Mmis n bnadem uřa d Bab n ssebt.” \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt Mt. 12:8; Lk. 6:5. \x*
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Asgenfi deg wass n ssebt
\m 
\v 1 Uca yudef-dd Yasuɛ ɛawed ɣar temzida. Tuɣa din ijj n weryaz, afus nnes iqucceḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt [Mt. 12:9-14; Lk. 6:6-11] — Mt. 12:9; Lk. 6:6. \x*
\v 2 Bdan ḥeṭṭan t, ma ad taɣ ad t issgenfa di ssebt, ḥima zemmaren ad zzayes cetcan.
\v 3 Inna as i weryaz wenni ɣar iǧa afus iqucceḥ: “Bedd di řwesṭ.”
\v 4 Xenni inna asen ɛawed: “Ma iḥeǧeř \add i bnadem\add* di ssebt, maḥend ad igg řxar niɣ řɣar, ad issenjem ijj n řeɛmar niɣ ad t yareddeǧ?” \add Maca\add* nitni sqaren.
\v 5 Ixzar ɣar yinni d as dd-innḍen s tefqeḥt zi ssibbet n řeqsaḥet n wuřawen nsen, uca inna i weryaz: “Swiẓẓeḍ afus nnec!” Isswiẓẓeḍ i-t-i-dd, idweř ufus nnes iṣeḥḥ ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt 1 Ij. 13:6; Mt. 12:13; Lk. 6:10\x*
\v 6 Řexdenni ffɣen Ifarisiyyen ak-d ca zi taddart n Hirudus, uca mcawaren xas, mammec ɣa ggen ad t areddǧen. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Mt. 12:14; Yḥ. 10:39; 11:53. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ isscen ṣṣulṭa nnes x řaryaḥ imengas
\m 
\v 7 Iffeɣ Yasuɛ ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes ɣar řebḥar, uca yarni iḍeffar i-t-dd řɣaci aṭṭas zi Ljalil, zi Yahudiyya, \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Mt. 4:25; Lk. 6:17. \x*
\v 8 zi Urcalim, zi Idumiya, zeg ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, zi Ṣur u zi Ṣaydun. Aqa ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran yusa-dd ɣares, minzi nitni sřin marra min igga.
\v 9 Inna i imeḥḍaren nnes maḥend ad awyen ict n tɣarrabut ɣares s ssibbet n řɣaci, ḥima war t ddeḥḥsen.
\v 10 Minzi tuɣa issgenfa \add din\add* aṭṭas, ařami xas wḍan ḥima ad t awḍen ad t ḥadan.
\v 11 Inni ittwajeyyḥen zi řaryaḥ imengas, wḍan zzates ɣar iḍaren nnes, řami t ẓrin, sɣuyen, nnan: “Aqa Cek d Mmis n AREBBI.”
\v 12 \add Maca\add* iweṣṣa ten aṭṭas ḥima war xas ssuffuɣen řexbar.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ ixḍar tenɛac n rrusul nnes
\m 
\v 13 \add Xas uca\add* yuři ɣar wedrar, iřaɣa-dd ɣares inni ixs, uca usin-dd ɣares. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt [Mt. 10:1-4; Lk. 6:12-16] — Mt. 10:1; Mk. 6:7; Lk. 6:13; 9:1. \x*
\v 14 Ifarz zzaysen tenɛac ḥima ad kides iřin u ḥima ad ten issekk maḥend ad barrḥen
\v 15 u maḥend ad ɣarsen tiři ṣṣulṭa x usgenfi n řehřac u x usuffeɣ n ccwaṭen.
\v 16 Cimɛun igga as Buṭrus, \add isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘aẓru’\add*,
\v 17 d Yaɛqub, mmis n Zabdi, d Yuḥanna, umas n Yaɛqub, isemma aten ‘Buwanirjis’, min ixs ad yini ‘ayt n wajjaj’,
\v 18 uca \add ifarz ɛawed\add* Andrawus d Filippus d Bar-Tulumawus d Matta d Tuma d Yaɛqub, mmis n Ḥalfa, d Tadday d Cimɛun, \add wenni umi ttkennan\add* Amɛessab,
\v 19 d Yahuda Isxariyuṭi wenni t i ɣa iɣdaren.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d Bᵉɛalzabub
\m 
\v 20 Usin-dd ɣar taddart uca inneyru din ɛawed řɣaci, ařami war ufin tawwart x macca n weɣrum. \x ◘ \xo 3:20 \xt [Mt. 12:22-32; Lk. 11:14-23; 12:10] — Mk. 6:31. \x*
\v 21 Umi sřin řaǧ nnes \add man aya\add*, ffɣen-dd, ḥima ad t ṭṭfen, minzi nnan: “Aqa ibbuhři.”
\v 22 Maca imseřmaden n idlisen inni dd-ihwan zi Urcalim nnan: “Aqa dayes ‘Bᵉɛalzabub’!” uca \add nnan:\add* “S umeqqran n ccwaṭen issuffuɣ ccwaṭen.” \x ◘ \xo 3:22 \xt Mt. 9:34; 12:24; Lk. 11:15; Yḥ. 7:20; 8:48, 52. \x*
\v 23 Iřaɣa asen-dd uca issiweř akidsen s imedya: “Mammec izemmar cciṭan ad issuffeɣ cciṭan? \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt Mt. 12:25. \x*
\v 24 Maɣar mařa temsebḍa ict n tgeldit x yixef nnes, war tzemmar tgeldit nni ad tbedd.
\v 25 Mařa temsebḍa ict n taddart x yixef nnes, war tzemmar taddart nni ad tbedd.
\v 26 Mařa ikkar cciṭan ḍidd i yixef nnes, xenni war ittiři d ijjen, uca war izemmar ad ibedd, maca ad yiři man aya d aneggar nnes.
\v 27 War izemmar ḥed ad yadef ɣar taddart n wenni ijehden maḥend ad ikecceḍ řeqcuɛ nnes, mařa war icarf wenni ijehden amezwar. Xenni izemmar ad ikecceḍ taddart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:27 \xt Mt. 12:29; Kul. 2:15. \x*
\v 28 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ belli ad asen ttwaɣfaren i tarwa n bnadem marra ddnub nsen uřa d aceqqef i zi ɣa ceqqfen, \x ◘ \xo 3:28 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:25; Mt. 12:31; Lk. 12:10; 1 Yḥ. 5:16. \x*
\v 29 maca wenni i ɣa iceqqfen di Arruḥ Iqeddsen war ɣares bu weɣfar qaɛ, maca aqa ittwaḥkem xas s řḥukm ittduman.” \x ◘ \xo 3:29 \xt 1 Yḥ. 5:16. \x*
\v 30 Minzi nitni nnan: “Aqa dayes řaryaḥ amengus.”
\b
\s1 Yemmas d aytmas n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 31 Řexdenni tusa-dd yemmas d aytmas, bedden barra i taddart, ssekken-dd ɣares, řaɣan as-dd maḥend ad ɣarsen dd-yas. \x ◘ \xo 3:31 \xt [Mt. 12:46-50; Lk. 8:19-21] — Mt. 12:46; Lk. 8:19. \x*
\v 32 Uca řɣaci qqimen nnḍen as-dd, nnan as: “Xzar, yemmac d aytmac aqa aten di barra, arezzun xak.”
\v 33 Yarra-dd xasen, inna: “Man ten i iǧan d yemma u man yen i iǧan d aytma?”
\v 34 Uca umi ixzar ɣar yinni ɣares iqqimen, inna: “Xzar, aqa yemma d aytma,
\v 35 minzi wenni itteggen min ixs AREBBI d netta d uma d učma d yemma.” \x ◘ \xo 3:35 \xt Yḥ. 15:14; 2 Kur. 5:16, 17. \x*
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Amedya n zzariɛet
\m 
\v 1 Ibda isseřmad ɛawed ɣar řebḥar u imun-dd xas řɣaci aṭṭas ařami yenya di tɣarrabut uca iqqim \add dayes\add* x řebḥar, am řɣaci marra tuɣa-t x tma n řebḥar x řbarr. \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt [Mt. 13:1-23; Lk. 8:4-15] — Mt. 13:1; Lk. 8:4 \x*
\v 2 Tuɣa isseřmad i-ten s imedya aṭṭas. Inna di tɣuri nnes:
\v 3 “Sřem! Xzar, ijj n ufeǧaḥ iffeɣ ḥima ad izarɛ.
\v 4 Am tuɣa izarreɛ, tewḍa ca \add n zzariɛet\add* x tma n webrid, ixecc-dd ijj n ujḍiḍ, ineqb i-tt.
\v 5 Tewḍa ca \add n zzariɛet\add* nneɣni x weẓru mani war dayes tuɣi bu ucař aṭṭas. Deɣya teɣmi s minzi tammurt war tuǧiɣ.
\v 6 Maca umi dd-tenqar tfuct, tecmeḍ, minzi war ɣares tuɣi bu weẓwar, xenni tisřaw.
\v 7 Tewḍa ca \add n zzariɛet\add* nneɣni jar isennanen uca mɣaren xas isennanen uca jeyyḥen tt, war tewci ca řɣiǧet.
\v 8 Tewḍa ca \add n zzariɛet\add* nneɣni x temmurt teṣbeḥ uca teɣmi, tegma, tewca řɣiǧet. Ca \add n zzariɛet\add* tusa-dd s třatin, ca s settin u ca s mya n tseqqar.”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Wenni ɣar iǧa imezzuɣen i useǧi, ejj i-t ad iseř.”
\b
\m 
\v 10 Umi tuɣa aten weḥḥedsen, sseqsan t inni d as dd-innḍen \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d tenɛac x umedya \add nni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt [Mt. 13:10-17; Lk. 8:9-10] \x*
\v 11 Inna asen: “Aqa immewc awem maḥend ad tessnem ssirr n Tgeldit n AREBBI, maca inni di barra ad asen yiři kuřci s imedya, \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Mt. 11:25; 2 Kur. 2:14; 3:14. \x*
\v 12 ḥima am ttwařan, ttwařan, \add maca\add* war ttwiřin, am ttesřan, ttesřan, \add maca\add* war fehhmen, ḥima war ttᵉtuben uca ad asen ittwaɣfar ddnub nsen.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Ica. 6:9-10; Mt. 13:14; Lk. 8:10; Yḥ. 12:40; Řex. 28:26; Rum. 11:8. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 Inna asen: “Ma war tefhimem ca i umedya-ya? Mammec i ɣa tessnem marra imettiřen-a? \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt [Mt. 13:18-23; Lk. 8:11-15]\x*
\v 14 Afeǧaḥ nni izarɛen, izarreɛ Awař. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Mt. 13:19; Lk. 8:11. \x*
\v 15 Ina aqa d inni x webrid, aqa yina d yinni daysen ittwazarɛ Wawař, \add maca\add* awarni řami d as sřin, řexdenni yusa-dd cciṭan uca ikkes Awař i ittwazarɛen deg wuřawen nsen.
\v 16 Uca yina d inni ittwazarɛen x temmurt uḥejri, aqa yina d inni xmi ɣa sřen Awař, ad t qebřen deɣya s řefraḥet,
\v 17 \add maca\add* war ɣarsen bu jjadira deg ixef nsen, ad qqimen ɣar ijj n řmijař \add waha\add*. Mařa temsar řmeḥnet niɣ umarret di ssibbet n Wawař, ad nqarḍen deɣya.
\v 18 Uca yina d inni ittwazarɛen jar isennanen, aqa yina d inni xmi ɣa sřen Awař,
\v 19 ad ɣarsen dd-adfent tḥissaf n ddunect-a d uɣekkʷi n wagřa d \add marra\add* nnecwat inneɣni, ad jeyyfent Awař, xenni idakkʷař \add Wawař\add* břa řɣiǧet. \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Mt. 19:23; Mk. 10:23; Lk. 18:24; 1 Tim. 6:9. \x*
\v 20 Uca yina d inni ittwazarɛen x temmurt iṣebḥen, aqa yina d inni, xmi ɣa sřen Awař, ad t qebřen, ad wcen řɣiǧet, ca \add zzaysen\add* třatin, inneɣni settin u inneɣni mya n tseqqar.”
\b
\s1 Amedya n řqendiř d řmerfeɛ nnes
\m 
\v 21 Inna asen: “Ma ad dd-asen s řqendiř, ḥima ad immars sadu řmud n imendi niɣ sadu qama? Ma war ittmarsi ca x řmerfeɛ? \x ◘ \xo 4:21 \xt [Lk. 8:16-18] — Mt. 5:15; Lk. 8:16; 11:33. \x*
\v 22 Minzi war din min inuffaren war dd-ittwassargeb, uca \add war din\add* uřa d ict n řḥajjet di tnuffra war tᵉtwasseḍhari. \x ◘ \xo 4:22 \xt Ayub 12:22; Mt. 10:26; Lk. 8:17; 12:2. \x*
\v 23 Mařa \add din\add* ḥed i ɣar iǧa imezzuɣen i useǧi, ejj i-t ad iseř.”
\b
\m 
\v 24 Inna asen: “Ḥḍam min ɣa tesřem. S řeqyas nni zzayes i ɣa teɛbarem, zzayes i d awem ɣa ɛbaren \add ɛawed\add*, uca i kenniw inni ittesřan ad asen immarni ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 4:24 \xt Mt. 7:2; Lk. 6:38. \x*
\v 25 Minzi wenni ɣar iǧa ad as immarni, u wenni war ɣar iǧi, uřa d min ɣares ad as ittwakkes.” \x ◘ \xo 4:25 \xt Mt. 13:12; 25:29; Lk. 8:18; 19:26. \x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n zzariɛet d Tgeldit n Arebbi
\m 
\v 26 Inna: “S uyenni ad tiři Tageldit n AREBBI am yijj n weryaz ineṭṭar zzariɛet di temmurt,
\v 27 xenni ad iṭṭeṣ, ad dd-ikkar, ǧiřet d wass. Uca zzariɛet ad tgeɛɛed, ad tegma, maca netta war issin mammec.
\v 28 Minzi tammurt tᵉttawi-dd řɣiǧet \add s yixef nnes\add*: amezwar aɣemmuy, xenni tidart, awarni as irden ikemmřen di tidart.
\v 29 Řami dd-tiweḍ řɣiǧet, řexdenni issekk amjar, minzi tameyra tiweḍ-dd.” \x ◘ \xo 4:29 \xt Yuw. 3:13\x*
\b
\s1 Amedya n tḥebbuct n zzariɛet n uxerdel
\m 
\v 30 Inna: “Min di i ɣa narwes Tageldit n AREBBI niɣ s man amedya i zi tt i ɣa narcem? \x ◘ \xo 4:30 \xt [Mt. 13:31-32; 34-35; Lk. 13:18-19] — Mt. 13:31; Lk. 13:18. \x*
\v 31 Aqa-tt am tḥebbuct n zzariɛet n uxerdel, tenni, řami tᵉttwazarɛ di temmurt, aqa nettat d tameẓyant x marra tiḥebba n zzariɛet i iǧan di temmurt.
\v 32 Awarni řami tᵉttwazarɛ, teɣmi-dd, temɣar x marra tibbi, ad tegg řefruɛ imɣaren ařami ijḍaḍ n ujenna zemmaren ad ggen řeɛwacc di tiři nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 33 Tuɣa Yasuɛ issawař awař akidsen s imedya aṭṭas am yina, s imedya ittřiqen maḥend ad ten sřen \add iwdan\add*.\x ◘ \xo 4:33 \xt Mt. 13:34. \x*
\v 34 Břa imedya war kisen issiweř ca, maca tuɣa issefham kuřci i imeḥḍaren nnes weḥḥedsen.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d tḥaryaḍt
\m 
\v 35 Deg wass nni, řami d tewḍa tmeddit, inna asen: “Ejj aneɣ ad neẓwa ɣar ujemmaḍin.” \x ◘ \xo 4:35 \xt [Mt. 8:23-27; Lk. 8:22-25] — Mt. 8:23; Lk. 8:22. \x*
\v 36 Semḥen di řɣaci, iwyen t umi t tuɣa ɛad di tɣarrabut, uca tuɣa din akidsen ɛawed tiɣarruba nneɣni.
\v 37 Uca tekkar-dd ict n tḥaryaḍt temɣar, řemwaj ccaten di tɣarrabut ařami tebda tᵉttcura.
\v 38 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ tuɣa iṭṭeṣ x ict n tsunta ɣar ḍeffar n tɣarrabut. Nitni ssfaqen t, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad nneɣ, ma war d ac necqi ca neccin mařa nettwahellek?”
\v 39 \add Xenni\add* ikkar, iwebbex asemmiḍ, inna i řebḥar: “Ars! Sqar!” Yarsa usemmiḍ uca idweř kuřci yarsa. \x ◘ \xo 4:39 \xt Ayub 26:12; Izhd. 107:29; Ica. 51:10. \x*
\v 40 \add Xenni\add* inna asen: “Mayemmi teggʷedem ammu? Min kenniw yuɣin war daywem bu l’iman?”
\v 41 Tudef i-ten tiggʷudi temɣar, nnan i wayawya: “Min iɛna Wa, aqa uřa d asemmiḍ d řebḥar ttᵉṭṭaɛen as?”
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n umeryaḥ
\m 
\v 1 Uca yiweḍ Netta ɣar ujemmaḍin n řebḥar di temmurt n Gadarinis. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt [Mt. 8:28-34; Lk. 8:26-39] — Mt. 8:28; Lk. 8:26. \x*
\v 2 Umi dd-iffeɣ zi tɣarrabut, iřqa i-t ijj n bnadem zeg imeḍřan dayes ijj n řaryaḥ d amengus.
\v 3 Tuɣa izeddeɣ deg imeḍřan uca war izemmar ḥed ad t icarf uřa s ssnaseř,
\v 4 minzi waxxa tuɣa carfen t aṭṭas n twařawin s iceddiyyen ɣar iḍaren u s ssnaseř, aqa netta iqḍu ssnaseř \add nni\add*, yarẓa iceddiyyen u war izemmar ḥed ad t iqemmeɛ.
\v 5 Tuɣa-t řebda, ass d ǧiřet, deg idurar u deg imeḍřan, isɣuyyu, iyezzem ixef nnes s iẓra.
\m 
\v 6 Umi iẓra netta Yasuɛ zi řaggʷaj, yuzzeř uca isjed as.
\v 7 Isɣuy s jjehd uca inna as: “Min din jar ayi akidek, a Yasuɛ, mmis n AREBBI, Amɛuǧi x kuřci. Ttzawgeɣ Cek s AREBBI, war d ayi ttmarrat!”
\v 8 Minzi aqa inna as: “Ffeɣ zi bnadem-a, \add a\add* řaryaḥ amengus!”
\v 9 Isseqsa t: “Mammec d ac qqaren?” Yarra-dd, inna: “Isem inu ‘Lixyun’, \add man aya ixs ad yini ‘Abarru’\add*, minzi neccin deg waṭṭas.”
\v 10 Izawg i-t aṭṭas ḥima war t issiggʷej barra i temmurt \add nni\add*.
\v 11 Tuɣa din ɣar wedrar ict n tḥimart temɣar n iřfan tᵉtthedda.
\v 12 Zawgen t ccwaṭen nni, nnan: “Sekk aneɣ ɣar iřfan, ḥima nzemmar ad daysen nadef.”
\v 13 Isamḥ asen Yasuɛ. Řexdenni ffɣen řaryaḥ imengas \add zeg weryaz nni\add*, udfen deg iřfan, uca tuzzeř tḥimart nni ɣar ijj n jjarf yuɛřan uca tewḍa di řebḥar. Tuɣa-ten ɛřaḥař deg wařfayen zzaysen uca ɣarqen di řebḥar.
\m 
\v 14 Maca imeksawen n iřfan arewřen, xebbaren man aya di tendint u x iyyaren. \add Iwdan\add* ffɣen-dd ḥima ad ẓaren min imsaren.
\v 15 Usin-dd ɣar Yasuɛ, ttwařan amaryaḥ i dayes tuɣa ccwaṭen, wenni di tuɣa izeddeɣ ‘Lixyun’, iqqim, yarḍ, s řbař nnes, uca ggʷeden.
\v 16 Inni iẓrin man aya, xebbaren ten min imsaren i umaryaḥ i di tuɣa ccwaṭen, u ɛawed x yiřfan nni.
\v 17 Uca bdan ttzawgen t maḥend ad iggʷej x temmurt nsen.
\m 
\v 18 Řami inya Netta di tɣarrabut, izawg i-t umaryaḥ i dayes tuɣa ccwaṭen ḥima ad iqqim akides. \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Lk. 8:38. \x*
\v 19 War t ijji, maca inna as: “Ruḥ ɣar taddart nnec d řaǧ nnec, xebbar i-ten marra min zzayek igga SIDI, mammec xak yarḥem.”
\v 20 Uca iruḥ, ibda ittbarreḥ di Dikapulis marra min d as igga Yasuɛ, uca marra tbehten.
\b
\s1 Yeǧis n Yayrus - Tamɣart tehřec řqedd n tenɛac n iseggʷusa
\m 
\v 21 Awarni řami iẓwa Yasuɛ s tɣarrabut ɣar ujemmaḍ, imun-dd xas ɛawed aṭṭas n řɣaci am tuɣa-t x tma n řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt [Mt. 9:18-26; Lk. 8:40-56] — Lk. 8:40. \x*
\v 22 Yusa-dd \add ɛawed\add* ijjen zeg imeqqranen n temzida, qqaren as Yayrus. Umi t iẓra, iwḍa as ɣar iḍaren. \x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Mt. 9:18; Lk. 8:41. \x*
\v 23 Izawg i-t aṭṭas, inna as: “Iǧi tmaẓuẓt tḥeřc aṭṭas. Ttzawgeɣ Cek ad dd-tased, ad xas tessarsed ifassen nnec, ḥima ad teggenfa, ad teddar.”
\v 24 Iruḥ akides uca iḍfar i-t-i-dd waṭṭas n řɣaci, uca nitni deḥḥsen t.
\m 
\v 25 Maca tuɣa \add din\add* ict n temɣart ttazzřen zzayes idammen tenɛac n iseggʷusa, \x ◘ \xo 5:25 \xt Lawi 15:25; Mt. 9:20; Lk. 8:43. \x*
\v 26 uca tekka xas tamara aṭṭas zeg iḍbiben umi tessuffeɣ marra min ɣares, \add maca\add* war testenfiɛ s walu, uca yarni ɛad xas řḥař.
\v 27 Aqa tesřa x Yasuɛ uca tusa-dd \add ɣares\add* am tekka x ddḥas n řɣaci zi ḍeffar nnes uca tḥada arruḍ nnes,
\v 28 minzi tenna: “Mařa ḥadiɣ mɣir arruḍ nnes, ad \add qqimeɣ\add* ddareɣ.”
\v 29 Řexdenni yuẓeɣ usizzeř n idammen, tuca ak-d arrimet nnes belli teggenfa zi řehřac nnes.
\m 
\v 30 Řexdenni yuca Yasuɛ ak-d Yixef nnes belli iffeɣ zzayes jjehd uca inneqřeb ɣar řɣaci, inna: “Wi iḥadan arruḍ inu?” \x ◘ \xo 5:30 \xt Lk. 6:19. \x*
\v 31 Nnan as imeḥḍaren nnes: “Cek twařid řɣaci ideḥḥes i Cek u Cek tesseqsid: ‘Wi d ayi iḥadan?’”
\v 32 \add Maca\add* iqqim ixezzar ḥima ad iẓar wi yeggin man aya.
\v 33 Tuɣa tameṭṭut teggʷed, tᵉttarjiji, am tessen min d as imsaren, uca tusa-dd, tewḍa as ɣar iḍaren uca tɛawed as tidett marra.
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* inna as: “\add A\add* yeǧi, l’iman nnem aqa iwca am tudart, ruḥ s řehna ad tiřid teggenfid zi řehřac nnem!” \x ◘ \xo 5:34 \xt Mt. 9:22; Mk. 10:52. \x*
\m 
\v 35 Am tuɣa ɛad issawař, usin-dd ca zi taddart n umeqqran n temzida, nnan as: “Iǧic temmut, mayemmi tṣeddaɛed ɛad Amseɣɣar?” \x ◘ \xo 5:35 \xt Lk. 8:49. \x*
\v 36 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ isřa awařen i innan uca inna i umeqqran n temzida: “War tteggʷed ca! Amen waha!”
\v 37 War ismiḥ uřa i yijjen ad t yuyur akides, mɣir Cimɛun Buṭrus d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna, umas n Yaɛqub.
\v 38 Usin-dd ɣar taddart n umeqqran n temzida uca iẓra i-ten ccaten agejdur, ttrun uca sɣuyyun.
\v 39 Umi dd-yudef, inna asen: “Mayemmi teccatem agejdur, tᵉttrum? Taḥenjirt war temmut ca, maca aqa tᵉṭṭeṣ.” \x ◘ \xo 5:39 \xt Yḥ. 11:11. \x*
\v 40 Nitni ḍeḥcen zzayes. \add Maca\add* Netta issuffeɣ i-ten kuřci barra uca yiwi akides babas d yemmas n tḥenjirt d yinni tuɣa akides, xenni yudef-dd mani tuɣa tᵉttwassars tḥenjirt.
\v 41 Iṭṭef deg ufus n tḥenjirt, inna as: “Kkar, \add a\add* taḥenjirt!”
\v 42 Řexdenni tekkar tḥenjirt uca tuyur, minzi tuɣa taḥenjirt ɣares tenɛac n iseggʷusa. Tbehten nitni s yijj n utebhet imɣar.
\v 43 Uca Netta yumur i-ten s jjehd, ḥima uřa d ijjen ad ibarreḥ s man aya. \add Xenni\add* iweṣṣa ad as wcen ḥima ad tecc.
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Anabi war ɣares bu ccan di temmurt nnes
\m 
\v 1 Iffeɣ ssenni, yusa-dd ɣar tendint nnes, uca ḍfaren t-i-dd imeḥḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt [Mt. 13:53-58; Lk. 4:16-30] — Mt. 13:53; Lk. 4:16. \x*
\v 2 Řami dd-tiweḍ ssebt, ibda isseřmad di temzida. Aṭṭas n yinni d as isřin, tbehten, nnan: “Zi manis dd-usint tmesřayin-a ɣar Wanita? Mana tiɣit-a i d as immewcen ařami msarent x ifassen nnes řeɛjayeb am tina?
\v 3 Ma war iǧi Wa d anejjar, mmis n Maryam, d umas n Yaɛqub d Yusis d Yahuda d Cimɛun? Ma war ǧint suyᵉtmas da akidneɣ?” U nitni nderfen dayes. \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Mt. 13:55; Yḥ. 6:42. \x*
\v 4 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna asen: “Anabi ɛemmarṣ war iǧi břa ccan mɣir di tendint nnes, jar řaǧ nnes u di taddart nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt Mt. 13:57; Lk. 4:24; Yḥ. 4:44. \x*
\v 5 Uca Netta war izemmar ad din igg uřa d ijj n řeɛjeb, illa issars afus nnes x drus n imehřac waha uca issgenfa i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Mt. 13:58. \x*
\v 6 Tuɣa ittebhet zi tikkest n l’iman nsen. \add Xenni\add* iruḥ, ittsara dcurat yudsen, isseřmad. \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Mt. 9:35; Lk. 13:22. \x*
\b
\s1 Asekki n tenɛac n rrusul
\m 
\v 7 Iřaɣa-dd i tenɛac \add n rrusul\add*, ibda issekk i-ten tyuya tyuya uca iwca asen ṣṣulṭa x řaryaḥ imengas, maḥend ad ten ssuffɣen. \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt [Mt. 10:1; 5-15; Lk. 9:1-6] — Mt. 10:1; Lk. 6:13; 9:1. \x*
\v 8 Yumur i-ten ḥima war kessin walu deg webrid mɣir taɣɣarct waha, lla ttesṭim, lla aɣrum, lla \add tipyisin n\add* nnḥas di tecyarin nsen, \x ◘ \xo 6:8 \xt Mt. 10:10; Lk. 9:3\x*
\v 9 \add maca\add* iwc asen ttesriḥ maḥend ad qqnen sandaliyat, \add maca\add* war yarrḍen tyuya n tcamirat. \x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Řex. 12:8. \x*
\v 10 Inna asen: “Mani ma tudfem ɣar ca n taddart, qqimem dayes, ař ssenni i ɣa teffɣem.
\v 11 Ɣar marra inni war kenniw iqbiřen u war ɣarwem ttesřin, zzerzem taɛejjajt zeg iḍaren nwem d cchadet i nitni. S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, ad yiři \add řḥař\add* ihwen i temmurt n Sadum d Ɛamurra deg wass n lḥisab zi tendint nni.” \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Mt. 10:14, 15; Lk. 9:5; 10:12; Řex. 13:51; 18:6\x*
\v 12 Uca ruḥen, barrḥen ḥima ad tuben.
\v 13 Ssuffɣen aṭṭas n ccwaṭen, dehnen imehřac aṭṭas s zzect uca ssgenfan ten. \x ◘ \xo 6:13 \xt Yaɛ. 5:14. \x*
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ
\m 
\v 14 Isřa xas ujeǧid Hirudus, minzi Isem nnes idweř icneɛ, inna: “Aqa Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ ittwassnekkar-dd zi taddart n imettinen, s uyenni ttwaggent zzayes řeɛjayeb nni.” \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt [Mt. 14:1-12; Lk. 9:7-9] — Mt. 14:1; Lk. 9:7. \x*
\v 15 Inneɣni nnan: “Aqa-t d Iliya!”, u inneɣni nnan ɛawed: “Aqa-t d nnabi am yijjen zeg inabiyyen!” \x ◘ \xo 6:15 \xt Mt. 16:14; Mk. 8:28; Lk. 9:8, 19\x*
\v 16 Řami isřa Hirudus man aya, inna: “Wa d Yuḥanna wenni umi qesseɣ azeǧif, aqa netta ittwassnekkar-dd zi taddart n imettinen.”
\v 17 Minzi Hirudus simant nnes, tuɣa issekk-dd \add ɣares\add* uca iḥebbes Yuḥanna, icarf i-t di řeḥbes x ssibbet n Hirudiyya, tamɣart n umas Filippus, tenni i-k-d imřec \add Hirudus\add*. \f ◼ \fr 6:17 \ft \bd afessar\bd* - Hirudus tuɣa d ařwes n Hirudiyya, tamɣart n umas Filippus.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:17 \xt Mt. 14:3; Lk. 3:19; 9:9. \x*
\v 18 Minzi Yuḥanna tuɣa iqqar i Hirudus: “War d ac iḥeǧeř ad ɣarek tiři temɣart n umac.” \x ◘ \xo 6:18 \xt Lawi 18:16; 20:21. \x*
\v 19 \add S uyenni\add* tuɣa Hirudiyya tenḍar dayes tiṭṭawin uca tarezzu ad t tneɣ, maca war tzemmar,
\v 20 minzi Hirudus tuɣa itteggʷed zi Yuḥanna, issen belli netta d aryaz d amseggad d amqeddas u iḥeṭṭa xas. Isřa zzayes aṭṭas n tmesřayin, \add x min\add* tuɣa ittegg, uca ifarḥ ad as iseř. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt Mt. 14:5; 21:26. \x*
\m 
\v 21 Deg ijj n wass ittwassnen igga Hirudus ict n zzardet deg wass n třařit nnes i řḥukkam nnes i ɣarsen řemɣaret aṭṭas, i arruyas x wařef n řɛeskar u i imeqqranen n Ljalil. \x ◘ \xo 6:21 \xt Amz. 40:20; Mt. 14:6. \x*
\v 22 Uca tudef-dd yeǧis \add n Hirudiyya\add*, tecḍeḥ, teɛjeb as i Hirudus d yinni iqqimen akides. Xenni inna as ujeǧid i tḥenjirt: “Ttar zzayi marra min texsed, ad am t wceɣ!”
\v 23 Ijjuǧ as: “Mecḥař ma zzayi i ɣa tᵉttared, ad am t wceɣ, waxxa ař azyen n tgeldit inu!” \x ◘ \xo 6:23 \xt Řqḍ. 11:30; Ist. 7:2\x*
\v 24 Teffeɣ-dd nettat, tenna i yemmas: “Min d as i ɣa ttareɣ?” Tenna as tanita: “Azeǧif n Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ.”
\v 25 Tudef deɣya s tazřa ɣar ujeǧid, tenna as: “Xseɣ ad ayi dd-tessarsed di tsaɛɛet-a azeǧif n Yuḥanna x ijj n ṭṭebṣi.”
\v 26 Icḍen ujeǧid aṭṭas, maca x ssibbet n tjaǧit u x ssibbet n \add inewjiwen\add* i iqqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add*, war ixs ad tt iqemmeɛ,
\v 27 u řexdenni issekk ujeǧid ijj n uɛessas ɣar řeḥbes s ssif, yumur ḥima ad dd-yawi azeǧif n Yuḥanna. Wanita iruḥ, iqess as azeǧif i Yuḥanna di řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 6:27 \xt Mt. 14:10. \x*
\v 28 \add Xas uca\add* yiwi-dd \add azeǧif nnes\add* x ṭṭebṣi, iwca as t i tḥenjirt u taḥenjirt tewc as t i yemmas.
\v 29 Řami sřin imeḥḍaren nnes man aya, usin-dd, ksin řxecbet nnes, ssarsen tt deg wenḍeř.
\b
\s1 Lmuɛjiza n usecci amezwaru
\m 
\v 30 Munen rrusul ɛawed ɣar Yasuɛ, xebbaren t x kuřci, x min ggin d x min tuɣa sseřmaden. \f ◼ \fr 6:30 \fk rrusul\ft - niɣ ‘imazanen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:30 \xt [Mt. 14:13-21; Lk. 9:10-17; Yḥ. 6:1-14] — Lk. 9:10. \x*
\v 31 Inna asen: “Asem-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nraḥ weḥḥedneɣ ɣar ijj n wemcan ixřan, \add ḥima\add* ad tareyyḥem cwayt!” Minzi tuɣa din aṭṭas n yinni dd-yusin d n yinni iruḥen, ařami war iwiḍen ad ccen. \x ◘ \xo 6:31 \xt Mk. 3:20. \x*
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* ruḥen weḥḥedsen di tɣarrabut ɣar ijj n wemcan ixřan. \x ◘ \xo 6:32 \xt Mt. 14:13; Lk. 9:10; Yḥ. 6:1. \x*
\v 33 \add Maca\add* řɣaci iẓra i-ten ffɣen-dd \add di tɣarrabut\add* uca aṭṭas i-t ɛeqřen. Uca izwaren as am ttazzřen x iḍaren ɣar dinni zi marra tineddam.
\m 
\v 34 Umi dd-iḍra Yasuɛ, iẓra aṭṭas n řɣaci, zziǧzen as, minzi tuɣa aten am wuǧi břa ameksaw. \add Xenni\add* ibda ad ten isseřmed aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 6:34 \xt Irm. 23:1; Ḥiz. 34:2; Mt. 9:36; 14:4; Lk. 9:11. \x*
\m 
\v 35 Rami iruḥ wass ad iqḍa, qarrben-dd ɣares imeḥḍaren nnes, nnan as: “Amcan-a ixřa u řweqt teɛdu. \x ◘ \xo 6:35 \xt Mt. 14:15; Lk. 9:12; Yḥ. 6:5. \x*
\v 36 Sekk i-ten ḥima ad raḥen ɣar řeɛraṣiyyat u ɣar dcurat yudsen, ḥima ad sɣen aɣrum i yixef nsen, minzi war ɣarsen min ɣa ccen.”
\v 37 Maca Netta inna asen: “Wcem asen kenniw min ɣa ccen!” Nnan as: “Ma ad nraḥ maḥend ad asen nseɣ aɣrum s mitayen dinar uca ad asen newc min ɣa ccen?”
\v 38 Inna asen: “Ruḥem, xzarem mecḥař n tecnifin i ɣarwem danita!” Umi argben, nnan as: “Xemsa n tecnifin n weɣrum d tnayen n iseřman.” \x ◘ \xo 6:38 \xt Mt. 14:17; Mk. 8:5; Lk. 9:13; Yḥ. 6:9. \x*
\m 
\v 39 Yumur i-ten ad \add ten\add* ssɣimen marra di tɛurricin x arbiɛ \add aziza\add*.
\v 40 Uca qqimen di tɛurricin n mya u di tɛurricin n xemsin.
\v 41 Umi iksi \add Yeccu\add* xemsa n tecnifin d tnayen n iseřman \add nni\add*, issgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnes ɣar ujenna, ibarek uca yarẓa ticnifin, iwca i-tent i imeḥḍaren nnes, ḥima ad tent ssarsen zzatsen. \add Ammu i\add* farqen nitni \add ɛawed\add* tnayen n iseřman i marra.
\v 42 Ccin marra, jjiwnen.
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* řeqḍen iřeqqʷaz iceṭṭen, ccuren tenɛac n tsuǧatin, uřa d iseřman \add iceṭṭen\add*.
\v 44 Inni iccin zi tecnifin tuɣa aten di xemsa-ařaf n yeryazen.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ iggur x waman n řebḥar
\m 
\v 45 Řexdenni iziyyar x imeḥḍaren nnes maḥend ad adfen ɣar tɣarrabut, ad as izwaren ɣar ujemmaḍ, ɣar Bayt-Ṣayda am isqad Netta řɣaci. \x ◘ \xo 6:45 \xt [Mt. 14:22-33; Yḥ. 6:16-21] — Mt. 14:22; Yḥ. 6:17. \x*
\v 46 Uca \add awarni řami\add* ten isqad, iruḥ ɣar wedrar ḥima ad iẓẓaǧ. \x ◘ \xo 6:46 \xt Mt. 14:23; Lk. 6:12. \x*
\v 47 Řami dd-tewḍa tmeddit tuɣa taɣarrabut di řbuɣaz uca Netta tuɣa weḥḥdes x řbarr. \x ◘ \xo 6:47 \xt Mt. 14:23; Yḥ. 6:16. \x*
\v 48 Iẓra belli nitni ttemqetmaren s uqeddef \add n tɣarrabut\add*, minzi asemmiḍ yusa asen-dd deg uɣembub. Ɣar ḥeṭṭu wiss arebɛa n ǧiřet yusa-dd ɣarsen Yasuɛ, iggur x wawan n řebḥar, uca tuɣa ixs ad ten iɛdu.
\v 49 Umi t ẓrin iggur di řebḥar, ittɣiř asen d řexyař aɣeddar uca sɣuyen, \x ◘ \xo 6:49 \xt Mt. \x*
\v 50 minzi marra ẓrin t uca nnxeřɛen. Řexdenni issiweř akidsen, inna asen: “Ggem uř! Aqa d NECC, war teggʷedem ca!”
\v 51 Inyi-dd ɣarsen di tɣarrabut uca yarsa usemmiḍ. Tuɣa nitni ttbehten, arewwɛen aṭṭas deg yixef nsen,
\v 52 minzi war fhimen walu i \add lmuɛjiza n\add* tecnifin, minzi uř nsen tuɣa iqseḥ.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n waṭṭas n iwdan di Jinisaret
\m 
\v 53 Awarni řami ẓwan ɣar ujemmaḍ, usin-dd ɣar temmurt n Jinnisaret. \x ◘ \xo 6:53 \xt [Mt. 14:34-36] — Mt. 14:3. \x*
\v 54 Umi dd-ffɣen zi tɣarrabut, ɛeqřen t iwdan deɣya.
\v 55 Uzzřen ɣar marra jjwayeh nni uca bdan ad dd-awyen inni tuɣa iheřcen aṭṭas di tassut ɣar wemcan mani sřin aqa-t Netta.
\v 56 Mani ma dd-yusa, di tendint niɣ di ředcur niɣ di řeɛraṣiyyat, ssrusan \add as-dd\add* imehřac deg ibriden uca ttzawagen t ad asen ismeḥ ad ḥadan mɣir abeḥřuř n ujeǧab nnes, u marra inni t iḥadan, ggenfan.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Ccariɛa d tubbart n iwdan
\m 
\v 1 Munen ɣares Ifarisiyyen d imseřmaden n idlisen i dd-yusin zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt [Mt. 15:1-20] — Mt. 15:1. \x*
\v 2 \add Umi\add* ẓrin belli ca n imeḥḍaren nnes ccin aɣrum břa ggin ad ssirden ifassen nsen \add d amezwaru\add*, ɛeyyben xasen.
\v 3 Minzi marra Ifarisiyyen d Wudayen war ttᵉtten mɣir awarni řami ssirden ifassen s yijj n řuḍu mliḥ, minzi tteṭṭfen di tubbart n imɣaren.
\v 4 U řami dd-usin zi ssuq, war ttᵉtten mařa war ssɣeḍṣen \add ifassen nsen di tbanyut\add* d amezwaru, u aqa din aṭṭas n tmesřayin nneɣni qebřen tent, maḥend ad zzaysent ṭṭfen \add ɛlaḥsab tubbart nsen\add*, am useɣḍas n řkisan d teydurin d tebriqin n nnḥas d \add dduri\add* n řectawat \add deg ict n tbanyut\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:4 \xt Lk. 11::38\x*
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* sseqsan t Ifarisiyyen d imseřmaden n idlisen: “Mayemmi war ḍfaren imeḥḍaren nnec tubbart n imɣaren, maca ttᵉtten aɣrum am war ssiriden ifassen?”
\v 6 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Nican inebba Icaɛya xawem, \add a\add* imnafqen, am mammec tura:
\b
\m \qt ‘Řgens-a iweqqar ayi s iyencicen nnes,\qt*
\m \qt maca uř nsen iggʷej xafi!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Ica. 29:13; Ḥiz. 33:31. \x*
\m 
\v 7 \qt Maca nitni cennɛen ayi baṭeř,\qt*
\m \qt minzi sseřmaden tiɣuriwin\qt*
\m \qt tinni d tiweṣṣa n iwdan.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Mt. 15:9; Kul. 2:18, 20; Tit. 1:14. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 8 Minzi tejjim tawṣeyyet n AREBBI, tᵉṭṭfem di tubbart n iwdan, am useɣḍas n řkisan d teydurin \add deg ict n tbanyut\add* u aṭṭas n tmesřayin nneɣni am tina.”
\v 9 Inna asen: “Nican aqa tneṭṭařem tawṣeyyet n AREBBI, ḥima ad teqqimem tᵉttᵉṭṭfem di tubbart nwem.
\v 10 Minzi Musa inna: ‘Weqqar babac d yemmac!’, u: ‘Wenni i ɣa ixzan babas niɣ yemmas, ittxeṣṣa as ad immet.’ \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Uf. 20:12; 21:17; Lawi 20:9; Aɛwd. 5:16; 27:16; Awřn. 20:20; Afa. 6:2. \x*
\v 11 Maca kenniw teqqarem: ‘Mařa ijj n weryaz inna i babas niɣ i yemmas: Min ma tzemmarem ad zzayi testenfɛem, aqa ggiɣ t d ṣṣedqet!’,
\v 12 ammu war t tᵉttejjim qaɛ ad igg ca i babas d yemmas.
\v 13 \add Ammu i\add* tesseḥqaram Awař n AREBBI s tubbart nwem i tᵉttsellamem, u tᵉtteggem aṭṭas n tmesřayin am tina.” \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt Mt. 15:6; 1 Tim. 4:3; 2 Tim. 3:2. \x*
\b
\s1 Tazdugi n wuř
\m 
\v 14 Iřaɣa-dd Yasuɛ ɣares marra řɣaci, inna asen: “Sřem-dd ɣari marra uca fehmem \add man aya mliḥ\add*: \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Mt. 15:10. \x*
\v 15 War din uřa d ict n řḥajjet i dd-ittadfen ɣar bnadem zi barra tzemmar ad t tessexmej. Maca min i dd-itteffɣen zi bnadem, aqa man aya issexmaj bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 7:15 \xt Řex. 10:15; Rum. 14:17, 20; Tit. 1:15. \x*
\v 16 Wenni ɣar ǧan imezzuɣen i useǧi, ejj i-t ad iseř.”
\m 
\v 17 Umi dd-yudef ɣar taddart, iggwej x řɣaci, sseqsan t imeḥḍaren nnes x umedya \add nni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt Mt. 15:15. \x*
\v 18 Inna asen: “Ma kenniw ɛad břa řefhamet? Ma war tefhimem ca belli marra min ɣa yadfen bnadem zi barra, war izemmar ad t issexmej,
\v 19 minzi man aya war dd-ittidef ca ɣar wuř nnes, maca ɣar uɛeddis, xenni ad iffeɣ ɣar wemcan nnes, ař ittwassizdeg marra macca.”
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Min i dd-itteffɣen zi bnadem d man aya issxemmaj bnadem.
\v 21 Minzi zi daxeř, zeg wuřawen n iwdan i dd-itteffɣen inwayen iɛeffanen: zzina, farq-ccɣeř, tukkarḍa, anɣay, \x ◘ \xo 7:21 \xt Amz. 6:5; 8:21; Awřn. 6:14; Irm. 17:9. \x*
\v 22 ṭṭmeɛ, řɣar, taḥraymect, afucceḥ, tiṭṭ taɛeffant, aceqqef, tuffet d tubbuheřya.
\v 23 Marra timesřayin-a tiɛeffanin tteffɣent-i-dd zi daxeř uca ssxemmajent bnadem.”
\b
\s1 L’iman n temɣart di temmurt n Ṣur d Ṣaydun
\m 
\v 24 Ikkar ssenni uca iruḥ ɣar temmurt n weymir n Ṣur d Ṣaydun. Řami dd-yudef ɣar ict n taddart, war ixs ad t issen ḥed, waxxa amenni war izemmar ad innuffar. \x ◘ \xo 7:24 \xt [Mt. 15:21-28] — Mt. 15:21. \x*
\v 25 Minzi ict n tmeṭṭut, ɣares yeǧis dayes ijj n řaryaḥ d amengus, tesřa xas deɣya. Nettat tusa-dd ɣares, tewḍa as ɣar iḍaren nnes.
\v 26 Tuɣa tamɣart-a d ict n temɣart takafriwt zi \add temmurt n\add* Finiqiya nni tuɣa d tasɣart n Suriya. Nettat tzawg i-t maḥend ad issuffeɣ cciṭan zeg yeǧis.
\v 27 \add Maca\add* Yasuɛ inna as: “Ejj iḥenjiren amezwar ad jjiwnen, minzi war ittřiq ad ittwakkes weɣrum n iḥenjiren ḥima ad immenḍar i yiṭan.”
\v 28 Maca nettat tarra-dd, tenna as: “Wah, \add a\add* Sidi, uřa d iṭan ttᵉtten iřeqqʷaz n iḥenjiren sadu ṭṭabřa.”
\v 29 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Uyur, minzi x ssibbet n wawař-a \add i tennid\add*, aqa iffeɣ cciṭan zeg yeǧim.”
\v 30 Řami dd-tusa ɣar taddart nnes, tufa yeǧis tezzeř di qama u cciṭan ittwassuffeɣ zzayes.
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n udehcur
\m 
\v 31 Iffeɣ-dd Yasuɛ ɛawed zi temmurt n Ṣur d Ṣaydun, yiweḍ ɣar řebḥar n Ljalil ɣar ṭṭarf n temmurt n Dikapulis. \x ◘ \xo 7:31 \xt Mt. 15:29. \x*
\v 32 Iwyen-dd ɣares ijj n udehcur, itewtaw, uca ttaren zzayes ad xas issars afus nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:32 \xt Mt. 9:32; Lk. 11:14. \x*
\v 33 Issiggʷej i-t zi řɣaci ɣar uɣezdis uca igga as iḍewḍan deg imezzuɣen nnes, issusef uca iḥada iřes nnes.
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* ixzar ɣar ujenna, izehhar, inna as: “Nurzem!”
\v 35 Řexdenni nnurzmen imezzuɣen nnes uca tefsi tesɣunt n yiřes nnes, \add ibda\add* issawař nican.
\v 36 Iɛřem asen war \add t\add* qqaren i ḥed, maca mecḥař ma ten yumur, waxxa amenni tuɣa ssuffuɣen xas řexbar mahu.
\v 37 Uca tbehten s unexřiɛ ařami nnan: “Marra igga i-t mliḥ! Yarra idehcar ttesřan d ignawen ssawařen.” \x ◘ \xo 7:37 \xt Amz. 1:31. \x*
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Lmuɛjiza n usecci i twařa wiss tnayen
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni, am tuɣa din \add ɛawed\add* aṭṭas n řɣaci uca war tuɣi ɣarsen min ɣa ccen, iřaɣa Yasuɛ x imeḥḍaren nnes, inna asen: \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt [Mt. 15:32-39] — Mt. 15:32. \x*
\v 2 “Aqa zziǧzen ayi řɣaci, minzi qqimen akidi \add ɛad\add* třata n wussan, war ɣarsen min ɣa ccen.
\v 3 Mařa ssekkeɣ ten ɣar tudrin nsen am \add ɛad\add* ǧuẓen, ad ttwaheyyfen deg webrid, minzi ca zzaysen usin-dd zi řaggʷaj.”
\v 4 Nnan as imeḥḍaren nnes: “Zi manis izemmar ḥed ad yaf aɣrum di řexřa-ya maḥend ad issjjiwen marra ina?”
\v 5 Isseqsa ten: “Mecḥař n tecnifin i ɣarwem?” Nnan: “Sebɛa.” \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Mk. 6:38\x*
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* yumur řɣaci ad iqqim di temmurt, uca iksi sebɛa nni n tecnifin, u awarni řami ibarek, yarẓa i-tent, iwca i-tent i imeḥḍaren nnes ḥima ad tent qeddmen, uca xenni qeddmen tent i řɣaci.
\v 7 Tuɣa ɣarsen cwayt n iseřman d imeẓyanen. Ibark i-ten ɛawed, inna ad qeddmen ina.
\v 8 Ccin, jjiwnen, uca yarwen min iceṭṭen, aqa sebɛa n tsuǧatin.
\v 9 Inni iccen tuɣa aten ɛřaḥař di arebɛa-ařaf.
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* issekk i-ten, uca řexdenni inya di tɣarrabut ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes, yiweḍ ɣar jjwayeh n Dalmanuta. \x ◘ \xo 8:10 \xt Mt. 15:39. \x*
\b
\s1 Antun n Ifarisiyyen
\m 
\v 11 Ffɣen Ifarisiyyen, bdan ttqacaḥen dayes, ttaren zzayes ict n řeɛřamet zeg ujenna ḥima ad t jarrben. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt [Mt. 16:1-12] — Mt. 12:38; 16:1; Lk. 11:29; Yḥ. 6:30. \x*
\v 12 Izehhar di Arruḥ nnes, inna: “Mayemmi ittettar jjiř-a ict n řeɛřamet? S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, ɛemmarṣ war d as temmewc i jjiř-a ict n řeɛřamet!” \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Mt. 16:4. \x*
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* ismeḥ daysen uca inya di tɣarrabut, uca ruḥen nitni ɣar ujemmaḍ.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Imeḥḍaren nnes ttun ad kisen ksin aɣrum, uca war tuɣi ɣarsen walu di tɣarrabut mɣir ict n tecnift n weɣrum waha. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt [Mt. 16:5-12] \x*
\v 15 Uca yumur i-ten, inna: “Xzarem, ḥḍam zeg wentun n Ifarisiyyen d wentun n Hirudus.” \x ◘ \xo 8:15 \xt Mt. 16:6, 12; Lk. 12:1. \x*
\v 16 Mcawaren jar asen, nnan: “D man aya minzi war \add ɣarneɣ\add* bu \add tecnifin n\add* weɣrum.”
\v 17 \add Maca\add* yargeb Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Mayemmi temcawarem belli war ɣarwem bu \add tecnifin n\add* weɣrum? Ma war tucim, ma war tefhimem? Ma ɛad uřawen nwem qesḥen? \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Mk. 6:52. \x*
\v 18 Ma ɣarwem tiṭṭawin, maca war tᵉttwiřim? Ma ɣarwem imezzuɣen, maca war tᵉttesřim? Ma war tɛeqqiřem ɛad?
\v 19 Umi arẓiɣ xemsa n tecnifin n weɣrum i xemsa-ařaf, mecḥař n tsuǧatin i iccuren s iřeqqʷaz i tyarwem?” Nnan as: “Tenɛac.” \x ◘ \xo 8:19 \xt Mt. 14:17, 20; Mk. 6:38; Lk. 9:13; Yḥ. 6:9. \x*
\v 20 “U ɣar sebɛa \add n tecnifin n weɣrum\add* i arebɛa-ařaf, mecḥař n tsuǧatin iccuren s iřeqqʷaz i tyarwem?” Nnan: “Sebɛa!” \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Mt. 15:36,37. \x*
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* inna asen: “Mammec ɛad war tefhimem ař řexxu?”
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n ijj n udarɣař di Baytṣayḍa
\m 
\v 22 Yusa-dd ɣar Bayt-Ṣayda uca nitni iwyen as-dd ijj n udarɣař, zawgen t ad iḥada wanita.
\v 23 Netta imneɛ adarɣař zeg ufus, indeh i-t barra i dcar uca issusef di tiṭṭawin nnes, issars \add xas\add* afus nnes, isseqsa min ittwařa. \x ◘ \xo 8:23 \xt Mk. 7:32. \x*
\v 24 Isewḍ, inna: “Ttwařiɣ iwdan gguren am ticejjura.”
\v 25 Xenni issars ɛawed afus nnes x tiṭṭawin nnes. \add Xenni\add* iggenfa, idweř ittwařa marra mliḥ.
\v 26 Issekk i-t ɣar taddart nnes, inna: “War d ttidef dcar, war t qqar i ḥed di dcar!”
\b
\s1 Cchadet n Buṭrus x Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Yasuɛ ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes ɣar ředcur n Qayṣariya-Filippus. Deg webrid isseqsa imeḥḍaren nnes, inna asen: “Min qqaren iwdan min ɛniɣ Necc?” \x ◘ \xo 8:27 \xt [Mt. 16:13-20; Lk. 9:18-21] — Mt. 16:13; Lk. 9:18. \x*
\v 28 Arrin-dd: “Yuḥanna Amseɣḍaṣ!”, ca nneɣni \add nnan\add*: “Iliya!”, inneɣni \add ɛawed\add*: “Ijjen zeg inabiyyen!” \x ◘ \xo 8:28 \xt Mt. 14:2; 16:14; Mk. 6:15; Lk. 9:8, 19 \x*
\v 29 Inna asen: “I kenniw min teqqarem xafi?” Yarra-dd Cimɛun, inna as: “Cek d Lmasiḥ, Mmis n AREBBI iddaren!” \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt Mt. 16:16; Yḥ. 6:69. \x*
\v 30 Yumur i-ten mliḥ, maḥend war \add tt\add* xas qqaren uřa i yijj.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes i twařa tamezwarut
\m 
\v 31 Ibda isseřmad aqa Mmis n bnadem ittxeṣṣa ad iweddeb aṭṭas uca ad ittwasseḥqar zeg imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen, ad t nɣen uca deg wass wiss třata ad dd-ikkar. \x ◘ \xo 8:31 \xt [Mt. 16:21-28; Lk. 9:22-27] — Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:18; Mk. 9:31; 10:33; Lk. 9:22; 18:31; 24:7. \x*
\v 32 Inna awař-a s bṭayṭay. \add Maca\add* iksi t Buṭrus ɣares ɣar uɣezdis uca ibda ittwebbex i-t.
\v 33 \add Xas uca\add* inneqřeb, ixzar deg imeḥḍaren nnes uca iwebbex i Cimɛun, iqqar: “Aggʷej xafi awarni ayi, \add a\add* cciṭan minzi cek war d ac icqi min iǧan n AREBBI, maca min iǧan n iwdan.” \x ◘ \xo 8:33 \xt 2 Ṣm. 19:22. \x*
\m 
\v 34 Iřaɣa-dd Yasuɛ i řɣaci ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes ɣares, inna asen: “Wenni ixsen ad ayi iḍfar, ad inkar ixef nnes, ad iksi ṣṣalib nnes uca ad ayi iḍfar. \x ◘ \xo 8:34 \xt Mt. 10:38; 16:24; Lk. 9:23; 14:27. \x*
\v 35 Minzi wenni ixsen ad issenjem tudart nnes, ad tt ixsar, \add maca\add* wenni i ɣa ixsaren tudart nnes di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n Řexbar Aṣebḥan, ad tt issenjem. \x ◘ \xo 8:35 \xt Mt. 10:39; 16:25; Lk. 9:24; 17:33; Yḥ. 12:25. \x*
\v 36 Minzi man řefḍeř n bnadem mařa yarbeḥ ddunect marra, \add maca\add* ad ixsar řeɛmar nnes?
\v 37 Minzi min ɣa iwc bnadem deg wemcan n řeɛmar nnes? \x ◘ \xo 8:37 \xt Izhd. 49:9. \x*
\v 38 Minzi wenni zzayi i ɣa iseḍḥan u zeg wawařen inu di jjiř-a izennan ixḍan, aqa uřa d Mmis n bnadem ad zzayes iseḍḥa, xmi dd ɣa yas s uɛuǧi n Babas ak-d lmalakat iqeddsen.” \x ◘ \xo 8:38 \xt Lk. 9:26; 12:8; 1 Tes. 2:19; 2 Tim. 2:12; 1 Yḥ. 2:23. \x*
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Asɛuǧi x wedrar ak-d Musa d Iliya
\m 
\v 1 Inna asen: “S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa ca zeg inni da ibedden war ttqasin ca řmewt ař ɣa ẓaren Tageldit n AREBBI ad dd-tas s jjehd.” \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt [Mt. 17:1-13; Lk. 9:28-36] — Mt. 16:28; Lk. 9:27. \x*
\v 2 Awarni setta n wussan Yasuɛ yiwi-dd \add akides\add* Buṭrus d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna weḥḥedsen ɣar ijj n wedrar yuɛřan, uca ibeddeř qibač i tiṭṭawin nsen. \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Mt. 17:1; Lk. 9:28. \x*
\v 3 Arruḍ nnes idweř yařeqq d acemřař aṭṭas am wedfeř, war izemmar uřa d ijj n bnadem x temmurt ad issemřeř amenni.
\v 4 Iḍhar asen-dd Iliya ak-d Musa am tuɣa ssawařen ak-d Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt Uf. 24:1, 9, 10, 16\x*
\v 5 Inna as Buṭrus: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, aqa mliḥ umi da neǧa, ejj aneɣ ad newwet třata n iɛuccuten n tseṭṭa, ijjen i Cek, ijjen i Musa u ijjen i Iliya.” \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Mt. 17:4; Mk. 9:5; Lk. 9:33\x*
\v 6 Maca tuɣa iweddar as min ɣa yini, minzi nitni ggʷeden aṭṭas.
\v 7 Ikka-dd useynu issduriy i-ten s tiři nnes, uca třaɣa-dd ict n tmijja zeg useynu, teqqar: “Wa d Mmi iɛizzen, sřem ɣares!” \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Aɛwd. 18:15; Ica. 42:1; Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 1:11; Lk. 3:22; 9:35; Kul. 1:13; 2 Bṭ. 1:17. \x*
\v 8 Umi ssgeɛɛden nitni tiṭṭawin nsen, deg ict n tecti war qqimen ttwařan ɛad ḥed akidsen, mɣir Yasuɛ weḥḥdes.
\m 
\v 9 Ařami dd-hwan zeg wedrar, yumur i-ten ḥima war ttɛiwiden i ḥed walu zi min ẓrin ař dd ɣa ikkar Mmis n bnadem jar imettinen. \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Mt. 17:9; Lk. 9:36. \x*
\v 10 Xemmřen awař-a deg yixef nsen am tuɣa ttseqsan ixef nsen min ixs ad yini \add wawař-a\add*: ‘Ař dd ɣa ikkar zi taddart n imettinen’?
\v 11 Sseqsan t, nnan as: “Mayemmi qqaren imseřmaden n idlisen belli ittxeṣṣa ad dd-yas Iliya d amezwaru?” \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Mal. 3:23; Mt. 11:14; Lk. 1:17. \x*
\v 12 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Aqa Iliya ad dd-yas d amezwaru uca ad yarr kuřci, uca \add ad tiři\add* am mammec tura x Mmis n bnadem, aqa ad iweddeb aṭṭas uca ad t sseḥqaren. \x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Izhd. 22:7; Ica. 53:4; Dan. 9:26, Asa. 11:4-7\x*
\v 13 Maca Necc ad awem iniɣ, Iliya aqa yusa-dd uca ggin zzayes min xsen am mammec xas tura.” \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Mal. 3:23, 24. \x*
\b
\s1 Abřiɣ dayes řaryaḥ amengus
\m 
\v 14 Řami dd-yusa ɣar imeḥḍaren, iẓra ijj n řɣaci d ameqqran ittenneḍ asen-dd u imseřmaden n idlisen ttqacaḥen ten. \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt [Mt. 17:14-20; Lk. 9:37-43] \x*
\v 15 Deɣya iẓra i-t marra řɣaci, tbehten aṭṭas, uca uzzřen-dd \add ɣares\add*, seǧmen xas.
\v 16 Xenni isseqsa imseřmaden n idlisen: “Min xef kidsen tᵉttqacaḥem?”
\v 17 Yarra-dd ijjen zi řɣaci, inna: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, iwyeɣ-dd mmi ɣarek. Aqa dayes řaryaḥ nni t yarrin d agnaw. \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Mt. 17:14; Lk. 9:37,38. \x*
\v 18 Řebda xmi t itteṭṭef, ineṭṭar i-t ɣar temmurt, itteffeɣ as-dd ukuffu zeg uqemmum, ittɣezza tiɣmas nnes uca ittaẓeɣ. Nniɣ i imeḥḍaren nnec ad t ssuffɣen, \add maca\add* war d as zemmaren.”
\v 19 Yasuɛ yarra-dd, inna asen: “\add A\add* jjiř war yuminen, mecḥař kidwem i ɣa qqimeɣ, mecḥař i kenniw i ɣa yarbuɣ ɛad? Awyem t-i-dd ɣari!”
\m 
\v 20 Uca iwyen t-i-dd ɣares. Umi t iẓra, řexdenni immenḍar i-t řaryaḥ, ařami iwḍa ɣar temmurt, ibda ittbarkikkiḍ, ittekk as-dd ukuffu \add zeg uqemmum\add*. \x ◘ \xo 9:20 \xt Mk. 1:26. \x*
\v 21 Yasuɛ isseqsa babas: “Mecḥař zeg wami t-i-dd-iḥkem uya?” Inna as: “Zi temẓi nnes.
\v 22 Aṭṭas n imuren ineṭṭar i-t di tmessi u deg waman ḥima ad t isshellek. Maca mařa tzemmared x ca, ɛawen ayi u ḥinn xafi!”
\v 23 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Mařa tzemmared ad tamned, aqa kuřci izemmar i wenni yumnen.” \x ◘ \xo 9:23 \xt Lk. 17:6. \x*
\v 24 Řexdenni isɣuy babas n uḥenjir s imeṭṭawen, inna: “Umneɣ, \add a\add* Sidi! Ɛawen l’iman ineqṣen inu.”
\v 25 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ řɣaci ittazzeř uca ssmunen-dd ɣares nitni, iwebbex řaryaḥ amengus, inna as: “\add A\add* řaryaḥ agnaw, Necc umureɣ cek: Ffeɣ zzayes! War ttdekkwiř dayes ɛemmarṣ!”
\v 26 Isɣuy cciṭan nni aṭṭas, ijebbed i-t aṭṭas ammu d wammu uca iffeɣ \add zzayes\add*. \add Xenni\add* idweř uḥenjir am yijj n umettin, ařami tuɣa nnan aṭṭas, aqa immut.
\v 27 Maca Yasuɛ iṭṭef i-t zeg ufus nnes, issbedd i-t.
\m 
\v 28 Umi dd-yudef ɣar taddart, sseqsan t imeḥḍaren nnes weḥḥedsen: “Mayemmi war nzemmar neccin ad t nessuffeɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 9:28 \xt Mt. 17:19. \x*
\v 29 Inna asen: “Ddegg-a war izemmar ad ittwassuffeɣ uřa s ict n řḥajjet mɣir s uẓummi d tẓaǧit waha.”
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes i twařa wiss tnayen
\m 
\v 30 Ffɣen-dd ssenni uca cuqen di Ljalil. Netta tuɣa war ixs ad t iɛqeř uřa d ijjen. \x ◘ \xo 9:30 \xt [Mt. 17:22-23; Lk. 9:43-45] — Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:18; Mk. 8:31; 10:33; Lk. 9:22; 18:31; 24:7. \x*
\v 31 Maɣar tuɣa isseřmad imeḥḍaren nnes, iqqar asen: “Aqa Mmis n bnadem ad immewc deg ifassen n iwdan, ad t nɣen uca awarni řami t ɣa nɣen, ad dd-ikkar deg wass wiss třata.”
\v 32 Maca nitni war fhimen i wawař-a uca ggʷeden ad t sseqsan \add x uya\add*.
\b
\s1 Man wen iǧan d ameqqran?
\m 
\v 33 Usin-dd ɣar Kafarnaḥum u awarni řami udfen ɣar taddart, isseqsa ten: “Di min di tuɣa tḥarrḍem ak-d wayawya deg webrid?” \x ◘ \xo 9:33 \xt [Mt. 18:1-5; Lk. 9:46-48] — Mt. 18:1; Lk. 9:46; 22:24. \x*
\v 34 Maca sqaren, minzi tuɣa ttemqacaḥen deg webrid di win iǧan d ameqqran zzaysen.
\v 35 Iqqim, iřaɣa-dd i tenɛac, inna asen: “Mařa ixs ḥed ad yiři d amezwar, ad yiři d aneggar uřa d amsexxar i marra.” \x ◘ \xo 9:35 \xt Mt. 20:27; Mk. 10:43. \x*
\v 36 Iksi aḥenjir, issbedd i-t di řwesṭ nsen, idarreɛ as, uca inna asen: \x ◘ \xo 9:36 \xt Mk. 10:16. \x*
\v 37 “Wi ɣa iqebřen \add mɣir\add* ijj \add n uḥenjir\add* am uḥenjir-a s Yisem inu, aqa iqbeř ayi u wi d ayi ɣa iqebřen, war d ayi iqebbeř, maca iqebbeř wi d ayi-dd-issekken.” \x ◘ \xo 9:37 \xt Mt. 18:5; Lk. 9:48; Yḥ. 13:20. \x*
\b
\s1 Wi war iǧin ḍidd nneɣ, aqa-t akidneɣ
\m 
\v 38 Yarra-dd xas Yuḥanna, inna as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, neẓra ijjen issuffuɣ ccwaṭen s Yisem nnec u nemneɛ i-t minzi netta war dd aneɣ iḍeffar.” \x ◘ \xo 9:38 \xt [Lk. 9:49-50] — Lk. 9:49. \x*
\v 39 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “War \add t\add* mennɛem ca, minzi war din uřa d ijj i ɣa yeggen timegga ijehden s Yisem inu, uca řexdenni deɣya ad xafi issiweř s řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 9:39 \xt 1 Kur. 12:3. \x*
\v 40 Minzi wi war iǧin ḍidd nwem, aqa-t akidwem. \x ◘ \xo 9:40 \xt Mt. 12:30; Mk. 9:39; Lk. 9:50; 11:23. \x*
\v 41 Wi kenniw i ɣa isseswen s yijj n řkas n waman waha, minzi aqa kenniw n Lmasiḥ \add i teǧam\add*, aqa s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, netta war ixessar ca řmunet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:41 \xt Mt. 10:42. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ iɛřem iwdan x min iɣekkʷan i ddnub
\m 
\v 42 Wi ɣa issenqraḍen ijjen zeg imeẓyanen-a i dayi yumnen, iḥřa as ad as tᵉttwagg ict n teṣḍart n tsirt tedqeř deg iri nnes, ad immenḍar di řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 9:42 \xt [Mt. 18:6-9; Lk. 17:1-2] — Mt. 18:6; Lk. 17:2. \x*
\v 43 Mařa issenqarḍ cek ufus nnec, qess i-t. Iḥřa ac ad tadfed ɣar Tudart d ameɛḍuř x wadaf s tnayen n ifassen di jᵉhennama, \x ◘ \xo 9:43 \xt Aɛwd. 13:7; Mt. 5:30; 18:8. \x*
\v 44 mani tikecca nsen war tᵉttmetti u timessi nsen war txessi. \x ◘ \xo 9:44 \xt Ica. 66:24. \x*
\v 45 Mařa issenqarḍ cek uḍar nnec, qess i-t. Iḥřa ac ad tadfed ɣar Tudart d aqejdaḥ x uweṭṭu s tnayen n iḍaren di jᵉhennama,
\v 46 mani tikecca nsen war tᵉttmetti u timessi nsen war txessi. \x ◘ \xo 9:46 \xt Ica. 66:24\x*
\v 47 Mařa tessenqarḍ cek tiṭṭ nnec, qeřɛ i-tt. Iḥřa ac ad tadfed ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI s ict n tiṭṭ x uweṭṭu s tnayen n tiṭṭawin di tmessi n jᵉhennama,
\v 48 mani tikecca nsent war tᵉttmetti u timessi nsent war txessi. \x ◘ \xo 9:48 \xt Ica. 66:24\x*
\v 49 Minzi kuř ijjen ad ittwameǧeḥ s tmessi u kuř taɣarṣt ad tᵉttwameǧeḥ s tmeǧaḥt. \x ◘ \xo 9:49 \xt Lawi 2:13. \x*
\v 50 Tameǧaḥt teṣbeḥ, maca mařa tameǧaḥt ixsar uředdi nnes, s min zi tt i ɣa ɛedřen. Ad tiři tmeǧaḥt daywem uca ḥḍam řehna jar awem.” \x ◘ \xo 9:50 \xt Mt. 5:13; Lk. 14:34; Rum. 12:18; Ɛbr. 12:14. \x*
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Yasuɛ issiweř x řemřac d waǧaf
\m 
\v 1 Ikkar, yuyur ssenni uca yiweḍ ɣar temmurt n Yahudiyya, ɣar wemcan n uẓekkwi n L’Urdun. Munen-dd xas řɣaci aṭṭas u ɛawed tuɣa isseřmad i-ten am mammec tuɣa innum. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt [Mt. 19:1-12] — Mt. 19:1. \x*
\v 2 Usin-dd ɣares Ifarisiyyen, sseqsan t ḥima ad t jarrben: “Ma iḥeǧeř i weryaz ad iǧef i temɣart nnes?”
\v 3 Yarra-dd, inna asen: “Min xef tuɣa kenniw yumur Musa?”
\v 4 Nnan: “Musa iwca ttesriḥ ad tᵉttwari tebrat n waǧaf maḥend \add aryaz\add* ad as iǧef.” \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Aɛwd. 24:1, 3; Irm. 3:1; Mt. 5:31. \x*
\v 5 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “X ssibbet n řeqsaḥet n wuřawen nwem aqa yura awem tawṣeyyet-a,
\v 6 maca zi beddu \add zi mani tᵉttwagg ddunect\add*, ixřeq i-ten-dd AREBBI d awtem d tewtemt. \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt Amz. 1:27, 2:24, 5:2; Mt. 19:4. \x*
\v 7 S uyenni ad ismeḥ weryaz di babas d yemmas, ad iqqen ɣar temɣart nnes, \x ◘ \xo 10:7 \xt Amz. 2:24; 1 Kur. 6:16; Afa. 5:31. \x*
\v 8 uca tnayen idsen xenni ad iřin d ict n ddat, uca ammu war ttiřin ɛad d tnayen, maca ad iřin d ict n arrimet. \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt Amz. 2:24; Mt. 19:5, 6; Afa. 5:31; 1 Kur. 6:16. \x*
\v 9 S uya min issmun AREBBI, war t ibeṭṭi bnadem.” \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt 1 Kur. 7:10. \x*
\m 
\v 10 Di taddart sseqsan t imeḥḍaren nnes ɛawed x man aya.
\v 11 Inna asen: “Wi ɣa iǧfen i temɣart nnes uca ad yawi tenneɣnit, aqa netta izna. \x ◘ \xo 10:11 \xt Mt. 5:32; 19:9; Lk. 16:18; 1 Kur. 7:10. \x*
\v 12 U mařa tamɣart teǧef i weryaz nnes, uca xenni ad tiři i weryaz nneɣni, aqa nettat tezna.”
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ ibarek iḥenjiren
\m 
\v 13 Iwyen as-dd iḥenjiren ḥima ad ten iḥada, maca imeḥḍaren webbxen inni ten dd-yiwyen. \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt [Mt. 19:13-15; Lk. 18:15-17] — Mt. 19:13; Lk. 18:15. \x*
\v 14 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ man aya, ixeyyeq, inna asen: “Jjem iḥenjiren ad ɣari dd-asen, war ten mennɛem, minzi Tageldit n AREBBI n yinni iǧan am nitni. \x ◘ \xo 10:14 \xt Mt. 18:3; 19:14; 1 Kur. 14:20; 1 Bṭ. 2:2. \x*
\v 15 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: “Wi war iqebbřen Tageldit n AREBBI am yijj n uḥenjir, aqa ɛemmarṣ war ɣares ittidef.”
\v 16 Idarreɛ asen, uca am xasen issars ifassen nnes, ibark i-ten. \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Mt. 19:15; Mk. 9:36. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d weryaz bu-wagřa
\m 
\v 17 Umi iffeɣ maḥend ad yuyur deg webrid, yuzzeř-dd ɣares ijjen, iwḍa as ɣar ifadden uca isseqsa t, inna: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar Aṣebḥan, min ɣa ggeɣ ḥima ad warteɣ Tudart ittduman?” \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt [Mt. 19:16-30; Lk. 18:18-30] — Mt. 19:16; Lk. 18:18. \x*
\v 18 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Mayemmi d ayi tᵉttřaɣid: ‘Aṣebḥan’? Uřa d ijj war iǧi d aṣebḥan, mɣir Ijjen waha: AREBBI!
\v 19 Cek tessned tiweṣṣa: ‘War zenni, war neqq, war tticar, war cehhed s ẓur, war ttɣecca, weqqar babac d yemmac.’” \x ◘ \xo 10:19 \xt Uf. 20:12-16; 21:12; Aɛwd. 5:16-20; Aɛwd. 24:14; Rum. 13:9. \x*
\v 20 Yarra-dd, inna as: “\add Wah, a\add* Amseɣɣar, aqa marra tina tuɣa ḍeffareɣ tent zi temẓi inu.”
\v 21 Ixzar dayes Yasuɛ uca issɛizz i-t, inna as: “Teqqim icten \add ɛad\add*: Uyur, zenz marra min ɣarek, ewc i-t i imezřaḍ uca ad ɣarek yiři ijj n řkenz deg ujenna. Xenni ksi ṣṣalib nnec, ḍfar ayi-dd!” \x ◘ \xo 10:21 \xt Mt. 6:19; Lk. 12:33; 1 Tim. 6:17. \x*
\v 22 Maca netta tuɣa iḥzen s wawař nni, uca iruḥ icḍen, minzi tuɣa ɣares aṭṭas n wagřa.
\m 
\v 23 Ixzar Yasuɛ ɣar imeḥḍaren nnes, inna asen: “Mecḥař iwɛar x yinni ɣar iǧa agřa ḥima ad adfen ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI!” \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt Awřn. 11:28; Mt. 19:23; Lk. 18:24. \x*
\v 24 Tbehten imeḥḍaren zeg wawařen nnes. Maca Yasuɛ iɛawed iṭṭef deg wawař, inna asen: “\add A\add* tarwa inu, mecḥař iwɛar x yinni ittcařan x wagřa nsen maḥend ad dd-adfen ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI!
\v 25 Ihwen ad yadef weřɣem zi tiṭṭ n tsineft zeg wadaf n bu-wagřa ɣar Tgeldit n AREBBI.”
\v 26 Immarni daysen ɛad unexřiɛ, nnan i wayawya: “Wi izemmaren \add xenni\add* ad ittwassenjem?”
\v 27 Ixzar daysen Yasuɛ, inna: “Ɣar iwdan war izemmar, maca ɣar AREBBI war iǧi amenni, minzi aqa ɣar AREBBI kuřci di tzemmar nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 10:27 \xt Ayub 42:2; Irm. 32:17; Zak. 8:6; Lk. 1:37. \x*
\b
\s1 Řmunet n weḍfar n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 28 Ibda Buṭrus ad yini: “Xzar, aqa neccin nejja kuřci, neḍfar i Cek-dd.” \x ◘ \xo 10:28 \xt Mt. 4:20; 19:27; Lk. 5:11; 18:28. \x*
\v 29 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ, inna: “S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: War din iǧi uřa d ijjen wenni isemḥen di taddart niɣ deg aytmas niɣ di yessmas niɣ di babas niɣ di yemmas niɣ di temɣart niɣ di tarrawt uřa deg iyyaren di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n Řexbar Aṣebḥan,
\v 30 i war ikessin mya n tseqqar. Řexxu di řweqt-a \add ad iksi\add* tudrin d aytmas d yessmas d tyemmatin d tarrawt d yeyyaren ak-d umarret, uca di zzman i dd ɣa yasen \add ad iksi\add* Tudart ittduman.
\v 31 Maca aṭṭas n yinni iǧan d imezwura ad iřin d ineggura, uca inni iǧan d ineggura ad iřin d imezwura.” \x ◘ \xo 10:31 \xt Mt. 19:30; 20:16; Lk. 13:30. \x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ issawař x řmewt d tnukra nnes i twařa wiss třata
\m 
\v 32 Tuɣa-ten deg webrid maḥend ad geɛɛden ɣar Urcalim u Yasuɛ tuɣa izwar asen. Nitni tuɣa ttbehten uca ggʷeden umi t-i-dd-ḍeffaren. Iksi tenɛac \add ɣar uɣezdis\add* uca ibda iqqar asen x min d as ɣa imsaren, \add inna\add*: \x ◘ \xo 10:32 \xt [Mt. 20:17-19; Lk. 18:31-34] — Mt. 16:21; 17:22; 20:18; Mk. 8:31; 9:31; Lk. 9:22; 18:31; 24:7. \x*
\v 33 “Xzar, neccin ad ngeɛɛed ɣar Urcalim u Mmis n bnadem ad immewc \add deg ifassen n\add* imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen, u nitni ad xas ḥekmen s řmewt, ad t sellmen i řegnus.
\v 34 Ad t sseḥqaren, ad t hettken s urekkuḍ, ad xas ssusfen, ad t nɣen, uca deg wass wiss třata ad ikkar.”
\b
\s1 Tutra n Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna
\m 
\v 35 Yusa-dd ɣares Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna, tarwa n Zabdi, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, nexs ad aneɣ tegged marra min zzayek ɣa nettar.” \x ◘ \xo 10:35 \xt [Mt. 20:20-28] — Mt. 20:20. \x*
\v 36 Inna asen: “Min texsem ad awem ggeɣ?”
\v 37 Nnan as: “Ewc aneɣ ad neqqim, ijjen ɣar ufusi nnec u wenneɣni ɣar uzeřmaḍ nnec, deg uɛuǧi nnec.”
\v 38 Maca Netta inna asen: “Aqa war tessinem ca min tᵉttarem. Ma tzemmarem ad teswem řkas i zi ɣa sweɣ Necc niɣ ad tᵉttwassɣeḍṣem s useɣḍeṣ i zi ɣa ttwassɣeḍṣeɣ Necc?” \x ◘ \xo 10:38 \xt Mt. 20:22; Lk. 12:50. \x*
\v 39 Nnan as: “Nzemmar!” Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Řkas i ɣa sweɣ Necc, ad t teswem, u aseɣḍeṣ i zi ttwassɣeḍṣeɣ Necc, ad zzayes ttwassɣeḍṣem, \f ◼ \fr 10:39 \ft \bd afessar\bd* - řkas i tuɣa iswa Lmasiḥ aqa-t d řeɛdab i iksi x ṣṣalib umi aɣḍab n SIDI ihwa xas di ṭṭweɛ n marra imednab i din iǧan u ad din iřin x řeḥsab ṣṣifet n Adam wenni ixḍan x SIDI AREBBI (xzar Ica. 53:4-7).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:39 \xt Mt. 20:23\x*
\v 40 maca aɣimi x yefus inu niɣ x uzeřmaḍ inu, war ɣari iǧi deg ufus inu maḥend ad t wceɣ, maca ad immewc i yinni umi ittwassewjed.” \x ◘ \xo 10:40 \xt Mt. 25:34. \x*
\m 
\v 41 Řami sřin ɛecra \add n imeḥḍaren\add* man aya, xeyyqen x Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna. \x ◘ \xo 10:41 \xt Mt. 20:24. \x*
\v 42 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa asen-dd Yasuɛ ɣares, inna asen: “Kenniw tessnem belli inni ittwaḥesben d řḥukkam n řegnus, aqa ḥekkmen xasen, u imeqqranen nsen, aqa ttṣeǧaḍen xasen. \x ◘ \xo 10:42 \xt Mt. 20:25; Lk. 22:25. \x*
\v 43 War ittiři ammu jar awem, maca wenni ixsen ad idweř d ameqqran jar awem, aqa netta ad yiři d amsexxar nwem, \x ◘ \xo 10:43 \xt 1 Bṭ. 5:3. \x*
\v 44 u wenni ixsen ad yiři d amezwaru jar awem, aqa netta ad yiři d amsexxar i marra.
\v 45 Minzi ɛawed Mmis n bnadem war dd-yusi, ḥima ad xas sexxaren, maca ḥima ad ixdem, ad iwc tudart nnes d aṣřaḥ i waṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 10:45 \xt Yḥ. 13:14; Afa. 1:7; Fil. 2:7; Kul. 1:14; 1 Tim. 2:6; Tit. 2:14. \x*
\b
\s1 Asgenfi n mmis n Timawus adarɣař
\m 
\v 46 Iwḍen-dd ɣar Ariḥa. Řami dd-iffeɣ Yasuɛ zi Ariḥa ak-d imeḥḍaren nnes d waṭṭas n řɣaci, tuɣa Timawus, mmis n Timawus, ijj n weryaz d adarɣař, iqqim deg webrid, ittettar. \x ◘ \xo 10:46 \xt [Mt. 20:29-34; Lk. 18:35-43] — Mt. 20:29; Lk. 18:35. \x*
\v 47 Umi isřa belli Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri aqa-t din, ibda isɣuyyu, iqqar: “\add A\add*, Mmis n Dawud, arḥem ayi!”
\v 48 Webbxen t aṭṭas ḥima ad isqar, maca netta iqqim isɣuyyu ktar: “A Mmis n Dawud, arḥem ayi!”
\v 49 Ibedd Yasuɛ uca yumur ad xas dd-řaɣan. Řaɣan-dd i udarɣař, nnan as: “Egg uř! Kkar, aqa ittřaɣa-dd xak!”
\v 50 Inḍar udarɣař ajeǧab nnes, ikkar uca yusa-dd ɣar Yasuɛ.
\v 51 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “Min texsed ad ac t ggeɣ?” Inna as udarɣař: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, ḥima ad twařiɣ.”
\v 52 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Xzar, l’iman nnec iwca ac Tudart!” Řexdenni idweř ittwařa, uca iḍfar \add i-t\add* deg webrid. \x ◘ \xo 10:52 \xt Mt. 9:22; Mk. 5:34. \x*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Adaf n Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim am ujeǧid
\m 
\v 1 Umi dd-qarrben ɣar Urcalim zeg uɣezdis n Bayt-Faji d Bayt-Ɛanya, zzat i wedrar n Zzitun, issekk tnayen n imeḥḍaren nnes, \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt [Mt. 21:1-11; Lk. 19:28-40; Yḥ. 12:12-19] — Mt. 21:1; Lk. 19:29. \x*
\v 2 inna asen: “Ruḥem ɣar dcar \add nni\add* qibač nwem. Xmi ɣares i ɣa tadfem, řexdenni ad tafem ijj n wesnus iqqen, war xas inyi uřa d ijj n bnadem. Fesyem as-dd uca awyem t-i-dd ɣari.
\v 3 Mařa inna awem ḥed: ‘Mayemmi i tᵉtteggem aya?’, xenni inim: ‘Aqa Siditneɣ iḥdaj i-t, uca řexdenni ad t-i-dd-issekk da \add ɛawed\add*.’”
\v 4 Nitni ruḥen, ufin asnus nni iqqen ɣar tewwart barra x webrid. Řami d as dd-arxun,
\v 5 nnan asen ca n yinni tuɣa din ibedden: “Min tᵉtteggem, tfessyem i wesnus?”
\v 6 Nnan asen am mammec ten iweṣṣa Yasuɛ, uca jjin ten.
\v 7 Iwyen-dd asnus ɣar Yasuɛ, ssarsen xas arruḍ nsen uca inya xas Yasuɛ \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt 2 Ij. 9:13; Yḥ. 12:14. \x*
\v 8 Aṭṭas ssun arruḍ nsen x webrid, ca nneɣni qessen-dd řefruɛ ak-d wafriwen zi tcejjura uca ssun ten \add ɛawed\add* x webrid.
\v 9 Inni t izwaren d yinni t-i-dd-iḍfaren, tuɣa sɣuyyun s jjehd, qqaren: “Uṣanna! Lbaraka i Wenni dd-yusin s Yisem n SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 11:9 \xt Izhd. 118:25, 26; Mt:21:15; Yḥ. 12:13\x*
\v 10 Ad tᵉttwabarek Tgeldit tenni i dd ɣa yasen s ufus n babatneɣ Dawud. Uṣanna di řuɛřa x řuɛřa \add n ijenwan\add*!” \x ◘ \xo 11:10 \xt Izhd. 118:25, 26; Mt. 21:9; Yḥ. 12:13 \x*
\v 11 Yusa-dd Yasuɛ ɣar Urcalim, yudef ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant uca iẓra marra \add min din imsaren\add*. Řami tuɣa issutem řḥař, iffeɣ ɣar Bayt-Ɛanya ak-d tenɛac. \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt Mt. 21:12, 14; Lk. 19:45; Yḥ. 2:14. \x*
\b
\s1 Anɛař n wartu
\m 
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes, řami dd-iffeɣ zi Bayt-Ɛanya, iṭṭef i-t-i-dd řaẓ. \x ◘ \xo 11:12 \xt [Mt. 21:18-19] — Mt. 21:18. \x*
\v 13 Umi iẓra zi řaggʷaj ijj n wartu n tazart ɣares tifray, yuyur din ḥima ad yarzu ma ad taɣ ad dayes yaf ca. Umi ɣares dd-yiweḍ, war yufi walu mɣir tifray, minzi war tuɣi bu řweqt n tazart.
\v 14 Iṭṭef deg wawař, inna as \add i wartu\add*: “Zi řexxu d tsawent war zzayem ittett uřa d ijj ɛad řɣiǧet.” Tuɣa imeḥḍaren nnes ttesřan \add min iqqar\add*.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d isebbaben di Taddart Iqeddsen
\m 
\v 15 Uca yudef Yasuɛ ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant n AREBBI, ibda issuffuɣ imsewwaqen d isebbaben \add nni iǧan\add* di Zzawect Tameqqrant, uca ibda issneqřab ṭṭwabeř n iṣarrafen \add n tmenyat\add* d řekrasi n yinni tuɣa iznuzan idbiren, \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt [Mt. 21:12-17; Lk. 19:45-48; Yḥ. 2:13-22] — Mt. 21:12; Lk. 19:45; Yḥ. 2:14. \x*
\v 16 uca war ijji ḥed ad iɛdu Zzawect Tameqqrant uřa s ict n řqecɛet.
\v 17 Tuɣa isseřmad, inna asen:
\b
\m “Ma war turi:
\m \qt Taddart inu ad as řaɣan\qt*
\m \qt ‘Taddart n tẓaǧit i marra řegnus?’\qt*
\m Maca kenniw tarrim tt
\m d ifri n iceffaren.” \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt 1 Ij. 8:29; Ica. 56:7; Irm. 7:11; Mt. 21:13; Lk. 19:46. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 Imseřmaden n idlisen d imeqqranen n ikehhanen sřin man aya, kkaren uca arezzun mammec ɣa ggen ad t nɣen, minzi ggʷeden zzayes, minzi řɣaci marra tuɣa ittebhet s useřmed nnes. \x ◘ \xo 11:18 \xt 7:19. \x*
\v 19 Řami dd-tewḍa tmeddit, ffɣen ɣar barra n tendint.
\b
\s1 Artu isřaw
\m 
\v 20 Di ṣṣbeḥ zic, řami dinni ɛdun, ẓrin belli wartu \add nni\add* isřaw zeg iẓewran.
\v 21 Cimɛun iften, xenni inna as: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, xzar, artu i tneɛřed, aqa isřaw.”
\v 22 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Maɛlik ad daywem yiři l’iman n AREBBI,
\v 23 maɣar s tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, mařa ḥed ad yini i wedrar-a: ‘Meksi, wḍa di řebḥar!’, war ittcekki deg wuř nnes maca ad yamen belli min inna ad iffeɣ, iwa aqa ad iffeɣ i netta am mammec inna netta. \x ◘ \xo 11:23 \xt Mt. 17:20; 21:21; Lk. 17:6. \x*
\v 24 S uyenni Necc ad awem iniɣ, marra min ɣa tᵉttarem am tᵉttẓaǧam, amnen belli ad t tkesbem, uca ad ɣarwem yiři. \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt Irm. 29:12; Mt. 7:7; Lk. 11:9; Yḥ. 14:13; 15:7; 16:24; Yaɛ. 1:5, 6; 1 Yḥ. 3:22; 5:14. \x*
\v 25 U xmi ɣa tbeddem tᵉttẓẓaǧam, ɣfarem min ɣarwem x ca n ijjen, ḥima ad awem iɣfar ɛawed Babatwem i iǧan deg ijenwan ddnub nwem. \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Mt. 6:14; Kul. 3:13. \x*
\v 26 Mařa war tɣeffarem kenniw, war d awem iɣeffar uřa d Babatwem i iǧan deg ijenwan i ddnub nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 11:26 \xt Mt. 18:35. \x*
\b
\s1 Aseqsi x ttesriḥ n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 27 Usin-dd ɛawed ɣar Urcalim. Am tuɣa iggur di Zzawect Tameqqrant, qarrben-dd ɣares imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add*. \x ◘ \xo 11:27 \xt [Mt. 21:23-27; Lk. 20:1-8] — Mt. 21:23; Lk. 20:1. \x*
\v 28 Nnan as: “S man ttesriḥ i \add zi\add* tᵉttegged timesřayin-a? Wi d ac iwcin ṣṣulṭa-ya ḥima ad tegged timesřayin-a?” \x ◘ \xo 11:28 \xt Uf. 2:14; Řex. 4:7; 7:27. \x*
\v 29 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Uřa d Necc ad kenniw sseqsiɣ ijj n useqsi, ḥima kenniw ad xafi tarrim, uca \add xenni\add* uřa d Necc ad awem iniɣ s man ttesriḥ i zi tteggeɣ aya.
\v 30 Aseɣḍaṣ n Yuḥanna, ma ikka-dd zeg ujenna niɣ zeg iwdan? Arrem-dd xafi!”
\v 31 Mcawaren jar asen, nnan: “Mařa nenna: ‘Zeg ujenna!’, ad yini: ‘Mayemmi war zzayes tuminem?’
\v 32 Maca mařa nenna: ‘Zeg iwdan!’, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad neggʷed zi řgens!”, minzi marra ḥesben Yuḥanna d anabi s tidett. \x ◘ \xo 11:32 \xt Mt. 14:5; Mk. 6:20. \x*
\v 33 Arrin-dd, nnan i Yasuɛ: “War nessin!” Netta inna asen: “Xenni uřa d Necc war d awem qqareɣ zi man ttesriḥ i zi tteggeɣ timesřayin-a.”
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Amedya n umarjuɛ n tzayart d ixemmasen iɛeffanen
\m 
\v 1 Ibda issawař akidsen s imedya: “Ijj n bnadem igga ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř, iẓẓu dayes tizayarin, iqewwar as-dd s ijj n wefray, iɣza tasirt n uḍiř, ibna dayes ṣṣumɛet uca iwekkeř \add amarjuɛ nni\add* i ixemmasen uca isafar. \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt [Mt. 21:33-46; Lk. 20:9-19] — Izhd. 80:1; Ica. 5:1; Irm. 2:21; 12:10; Mt. 21:33; Lk. 20:9. \x*
\v 2 Řami dd-yiweḍ řḥař, issekk amsexxar nnes ɣar ixemmasen, ḥima ad iksi \add tasɣart nnes\add* zeg weřqaḍ n umarjeɛ n uḍiř.
\v 3 Maca nitni wtin t uca ssekken t ixwa.
\v 4 Ɛawed issekk ɣarsen ijj n umsexxar nneɣni, arejmen t, marẓen as, uca řami t ssbeḥtřen, uẓẓřen \add xas\add*.
\v 5 Ɛawed issekk-dd ɣarsen wenneɣni uca nɣin t \add uřa d netta\add*. Ammu \add i issekk ɛad\add* aṭṭas n inneɣni, hettken ca zzaysen s urekkuḍ d ca nneɣni zzaysen nɣin ten.
\v 6 Ɣar uneggar issekk ɣarsen ayenni n mmis i ɣares i xas iɛizzen, maɣar inna: ‘Nican ad weqqaren mmi!’
\v 7 Maca ixemmasen, nni nnan jar asen: ‘Aqa d wa d awrit. Zidem, ad t neneɣ uca ad ɣarneɣ yiři řwart.’ \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt Amz. 37:17; Izhd. 2:8; Mt. 26:3; Yḥ. 11:53\x*
\v 8 Ṭṭfen t, nɣin t uca nḍaren t barra i umarjeɛ n uḍiř.
\v 9 Min ɣa yegg bab n umarjeɛ n uḍiř? Ad dd-yas, ad ineɣ ixemmasen uca ad iwc amarjeɛ n uḍiř i inneɣni.
\v 10 Ma war teɣrim \add awař-a n\add* Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*? ...
\b
\m \qt ‘Aẓru i tuɣa immenḍaren ibennayen,\qt*
\m \qt aqa idweř d \tl aẓru d\tl* Azeǧif n teɣmart.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:10 \xt Izhd. 118:22, 23; Ica. 28:16; Mt. 21:42; Lk. 20:17; Řex. 4:11; Rum. 9:33; 1 Bṭ. 2:6. \x*
\m 
\v 11 \qt Wa yusa-dd zi SIDI\qt*
\m \qt u man aya d řeɛjeb di tiṭṭawin nneɣ.’”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt Izhd. 118:22, 23\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 Xsen ad t ṭṭfen maca nitni ggʷeden zi řɣaci, minzi fehmen belli tuɣa issawař xasen s umedya nni. Nitni jjin t uca uyuren.
\b
\s1 Axeǧeṣ n ḍḍariba i qayṣar
\m 
\v 13 Xenni ssekken ɣares ca n yeryazen zeg Ifarisiyyen u ca zi taddart n Hirudus, ḥima ad as ṭṭfen s wawařen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt [Mt. 22:15-22; Lk. 20:20-26] — Mt. 22:15; Lk. 20:20. \x*
\v 14 Umi dd-usin, nnan as: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, neccin nessen aqa Cek d tidett, war teggʷided zeg iwdan u war txezzared ca ɣar wudem n iwdan, maca tesseřmaded abrid n AREBBI s tidett. Ma iḥeǧeř ad newc ddariba i kuř ijjen \add zzayneɣ\add* i qayṣar niɣ lla? Ma ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad nxeǧeṣ ḍḍariba niɣ lla?”
\v 15 Řami Netta yargeb x nnifaq nsen, inna asen: “Mayemmi d ayi tᵉttjarrabem? Awyem ayi-dd ijj n dinar ḥima ad t ẓareɣ!”
\v 16 Iwyen as-dd ijj \add n dinar\add*. Xenni inna asen: “Wi yiřan taṣwirt-a d tira-ya?” Nnan as: “N qayṣar!”
\v 17 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Wcem \add xenni\add* i qayṣar min iǧan i qayṣar, u min iǧan i AREBBI i AREBBI.” Uca ttɛejben dayes. \x ◘ \xo 12:17 \xt Mt. 17:25; 22:21; Rum. 13:7. \x*
\b
\s1 Aseqsi n Iṣaduqiyyen x tnukra
\m 
\v 18 Usin-dd ɣares \add ɛawed\add* Iṣaduqiyyen nni iqqaren belli war din bu tnukra. Sseqsan t, nnan: \x ◘ \xo 12:18 \xt [Mt. 22:23-33; Lk. 20:27-40] — Mt. 22:23; Lk. 20:27; Řex. 23:8. \x*
\v 19 “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, aqa yura aneɣ Musa, mařa immut i ḥed umas uca ijja tamɣart, \add maca\add* war dd-ijji bu tarrawt, ad yawi umas tamɣart nni uca ad dd-yejj aḥenjir i umas. \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt Amz. 38:8; Aɛwd. 25:5, 6. \x*
\v 20 Tuɣa din sebɛa n wawmaten. Amezwaru yiwi ict n temɣart uca awarni řami immut, war dd-ijji bu dduriyet.
\v 21 Xenni yiwyi i-tt wenni wiss tnayen uca immut, war dd-ijji bu dduriyet uřa d netta, uca ammu uřa d wenni wiss třata.
\v 22 Marra sebɛa \add nni\add* iwyen tt, war dd-jjin bu dduriyet. Aneggar nsen marra temmut temɣart \add nni\add* ɛawed.
\v 23 Iwa di tnukra, xmi dd ɣa kkaren, umi ɣa tiři temɣart nni? Minzi sebɛa \add nni marra\add* iwyen tt d tamɣart.”
\v 24 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ma war txeṭṭim ca minzi war tessinem ca Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* d jjehd n AREBBI?
\v 25 Maɣar xmi dd ɣa kkaren jar imettinen, war tent ttiwyen d tamɣart u war ssmiǧicen timɣarin i yeryazen, maca ad iřin am lmalakat \add i iǧan\add* deg ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 12:25 \xt Mt. 22:30; 1 Yḥ. 3:2. \x*
\v 26 Maca zi jjihet n imettinen aqa ttwassnekkaren: Ma war teɣrim deg wedlis n Musa, mammec akides issiweř AREBBI zi cbarq ak-d isennanen, inna: ‘D NECC d AREBBI n Ibrahim d AREBBI n Isḥaq d AREBBI n Yaɛqub’? \x ◘ \xo 12:26 \xt Uf. 3:6, 15; Mt. 22:31,32; Řex. 7:32; Ɛbr. 11:16. \x*
\v 27 Netta war iǧi d AREBBI n imettinen, maca \add d AREBBI\add* n yinni iddaren. S uyenni aqa kenniw txeṭṭam aṭṭas.”
\b
\s1 Tawṣeyyet tameqqrant
\m 
\v 28 Ijjen zeg imseřmaden n idlisen iqarreb-dd ɣares, isřa asen ttemharwaḍen jar asen uca issen belli Netta aqa yarra-dd xasen mliḥ. \add Xenni\add* isseqsa t: “Man tent iǧan d tawṣeyyet tamezwarut x kuřci?” \x ◘ \xo 12:28 \xt [Mt. 22:34-40; Lk. 10:25-28] — Mt. 22:34; Lk. 10:25. \x*
\v 29 Yarra-dd xas Yasuɛ: “Aqa tamezwarut x marra tiweṣṣa: Seř a Israil! SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, SIDI d Ijj. \x ◘ \xo 12:29 \xt Aɛwd. 6:4-5; 10:12; Lk. 10:27. \x*
\v 30 Ad texsed SIDI, AREBBI nnec s marra wuř nnec s marra řeɛmar nnec s marra řeɛqeř nnec s marra jjehd nnec. Ta d tawṣeyyet tamezwarut. \x ◘ \xo 12:30 \xt Aɛwd. 6:5; 10:12; 30:6; Mt. 22:37; Lk. 10:27. \x*
\v 31 U tawṣeyyet wiss tnayen, amecnaw tanita, aqa d ta: Ad texsed jjar nnec amecnaw ixef nnec. War din bu tewṣeyyet nneɣnit d tameqqrant x tina \add s tnayen\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 12:31 \xt Lawi 19:18; Mt. 22:39; Rum. 13:9; Gal. 5:14; Yaɛ. 2:8. \x*
\v 32 Inna as umseřmad n idlisen: “Nican, \add a\add* Amseřmad inu, s tidett tennid belli Netta d Ijjen, war din uřa d ijj nneɣni mɣir Netta,
\v 33 u belli mařa ijj n bnadem ad t ixs s wuř marra, s řeɛqeř marra, s řeɛmar marra u s jjehd marra, uca ad ixs jjar nnes amecnaw ixef nnes, aqa d man aya ḥsen zi marra tiɣarṣin n wecmaḍ d marra tiɣarṣin nneɣnit.”
\v 34 Umi iẓra Yasuɛ belli yarra-dd s řeɛqeř, inna as: “Aqa cek war tiggʷijed ca x Tgeldit n AREBBI.” Xenni war iɛewweř ḥed ad t isseqsa uřa deg ict n tmesřact. \x ◘ \xo 12:34 \xt Aɛwd. 6:4-5, 4:35; Ica. 45:21\x*
\b
\s1 Man wen iǧan d mmis n Dawud?
\m 
\v 35 Řami tuɣa isseřmad di Zzawect Tameqqrant iṭṭef Yasuɛ deg wawař, inna: “Mammec qqaren imseřmaden n idlisen belli Lmasiḥ d Mmis n Dawud? \x ◘ \xo 12:35 \xt [Mt. 22:41-46; Lk. 20:41-44] — Mt. 22:41; Mk. 10:47, 48; Mk. 11:10; Lk. 20:41. \x*
\v 36 Minzi Dawud s yixef nnes inna s Arruḥ Iqeddsen:
\b
\m \qt ‘Inna SIDI i Sidi inu:\qt*
\m \qt Qqim-dd x ufusi inu\qt*
\m \qt ař dd ɣa ggeɣ řɛedyan nnec\qt*
\m \qt d tanebdat sadu iḍaren nnec.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 12:36 \xt 2 Ṣm. 23:2; Izhd. 110:1; Řex. 1:16; 2:34; 28:25; 1 Kur. 15:25; Ɛbr. 1:13; 10:13; 2 Bṭ. 1:21 \x*
\b
\m 
\v 37 S uya ittřaɣa as-dd Dawud: ‘Sidi inu!’ Manis dd-ikka d mmis?” Marra řɣaci tuɣa isřa as s řefraḥet.
\b
\s1 Aɛřam ɣar řgens x Imseřmaden n idlisen
\m 
\v 38 Inna asen deg useřmad nnes: “Ḥḍam ixef nwem zeg imseřmaden n idlisen inni umi itteɛjib asen řḥař xmi ɣa uyuren s řeɛbayat tizirarin u xmi xasen i ɣa seǧmen \add iwdan\add* di řeswaq, \x ◘ \xo 12:38 \xt [Mt. 23:1-36; Lk. 20:45-47] — Mt. 23:5, 6; Lk. 11:43; 20:46. \x*
\v 39 inni \add umi itteɛjib asen\add* řekrasi n zzat di temzidawin, uřa d imucan imezwura ɣar imensiwen \add n wuraren\add*.
\v 40 Nitni ttetten tudrin n tijjař \add am ttᵉttaren\add* tiwhibin di ṭṭweɛ n tẓaǧatin nsen tizirarin. Aqa ina ad ksin řḥukm d ameqqran.” \x ◘ \xo 12:40 \xt Mt. 23:14; Lk. 20:47; 2 Tim. 3:6; Tit. 1:11. \x*
\b
\s1 Ṣṣedqet n tajjač
\m 
\v 41 Am iqqim Yasuɛ qibač i ssenduq n ṣṣedqet, iẓra mammec ineṭṭar řɣaci tinɛacin di ssenduq. Aṭṭas n aytbab n wagřa tuɣa neṭṭaren dayes aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 12:41 \xt [Lk. 21:1-4] — 2 Ij. 12:10; Lk. 21:1. \x*
\v 42 Tusa-dd ict n tajjač d řmeskina tenḍar dayes tnayen n uqiyyat, semman tent ‘camunat’. \f ◼ \fr 12:42 \fk camuna\ft - nettat d ijj nuṣuldi n Wudayen. Aqa tamɣart-a tenḍar dayes tnayen n camunat. Uqiyya qqaren as ‘camuna’ d ameẓyan x marra uqiyyat n nnḥas.\f*
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Yasuɛ i imeḥḍaren nnes, inna asen: “S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, tajjač-a řmeskina aqa tenḍar dayes ktar x marra iwdan nni inḍaren di ssenduq n ṣṣedqet. \x ◘ \xo 12:43 \xt 2 Kur. 8:12. \x*
\v 44 Minzi marra nḍaren dayes zi min ɣarsen aṭṭas, maca ta zi drus nnes tenḍar dayes kuřci min ɣares, aqa tenḍar marra min ɣares d agřa.”
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Abarreḥ n Yasuɛ x qeṭṭu n ddunect
\m 
\v 1 Ařami dd-iffeɣ zi Zzawect Tameqqrant, inna as ijjen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes: “\add A\add* Amseɣɣar, xzar, mammec ǧan iẓra-ya d řebni-ya!” \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt [Mt. 24:1-44; Lk. 21:5-33] — Mt. 24:1; Lk. 21:5. \x*
\v 2 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna as: “Ma teẓrid řebni-ya imɣaren? War da ittɣimi uřa d ijj n weẓru x weẓru nneɣni i war ittnehdim.” \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt 1 Ij. 9:7, 8; Mixa 3:12; Lk. 19:44. \x*
\m 
\v 3 Řami tuɣa iqqim x wedrar n Zzitun qibač i Zzawect Tameqqrant, sseqsan t Buṭrus d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna d Andrawus řami ten tuɣa weḥḥedsen: \x ◘ \xo 13:3 \xt Mt. 24:3; Lk. 21:7. \x*
\v 4 “Ini aneɣ meřmi i ɣa yiři man aya, u man ad tiři řeɛřamet aqa marra timesřayn-a ad awḍent?” \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Řex. 1:6. \x*
\m 
\v 5 Ibda Yasuɛ iqqar asen: “\bd Xzarem\bd*, ḥima war kenniw iɣekkwi ḥed. \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt Irm. 29:8; Afa. 5:6; 2 Ts. 2:2, 3; 1 Yḥ. 4:1. \x*
\v 6 Aqa aṭṭas ad dd-asen s Yisem inu qqaren: ‘Aqa d Necc!’, uca ad ɣwan aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Irm. 14:14; 23:21. \x*
\v 7 Mařa tesřim x imenɣan d řexbar n garrat, war ttnexřiɛem ca, minzi s uɣiř ad yiři man aya, maca war ittiři ɛad d aneggar.
\v 8 Minzi řgens ad ikkar ḍidd i řgens nneɣni u tageldit ḍidd i tgeldit nneɣni. Ad iřin inhezzan n temmurt zeg wemcan ɣar wemcan nneɣni uca ad yiři řaẓ d uɣewwuɣ. Timesřayin-a d beddu n řewjeɛ \add n tarwa\add*. \x ◘ \xo 13:8 \xt Ica. 19:2. \x*
\m 
\v 9 \bd Ḥḍam\bd* ixef nwem, minzi ad kenniw sellmen i tudrin n ccreɛ, ad kenniw hettken s urekkuḍ di temzidawin nsen uca ad kenniw ssiwḍen ɣar ijeǧiden d řḥukkam di ssibbet inu, d cchadet i nitni. \x ◘ \xo 13:9 \xt Mt. 10:17; 24:9; Lk. 21:12; Yḥ. 15:19; 16:2; Asa. 2:10. \x*
\v 10 Maca ɣar umezwar ittxeṣṣa ad ittwabarreḥ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan di marra řegnus.
\v 11 Xmi kenniw i ɣa gewwden ḥima ad kenniw sellmen, war kessim s wemnus qbeř zi min ɣa tinim, war dayes txarriṣem ca, \add maca\add* min ma d awem i ɣa immewcen di tsaɛɛet nni, siwřem zzayes, minzi war teǧim d kenniw i issawařen, maca d Arruḥ Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 13:11 \xt Mt. 10:19; Lk. 12:11; 21:4. \x*
\v 12 Umas ad isellem umas maḥend ad \add t\add* nɣen, u babas ad isellem mmis, uca ad tekkar tarwa x lwalidin nnes uca ad ten nɣen. \x ◘ \xo 13:12 \xt Ḥiz. 38:21; Mixa 7:6. \x*
\v 13 Ad kenniw carhen marra di ssibbet n Yisem inu, maca wenni i ɣa iṣbaren ař aneggar, ad ittwassenjem. \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt Mt. 10:22; 24:13; Lk. 21:19; Asa. 2:7, 10. \x*
\m 
\v 14 Xmi ɣa tẓarem nnɛi n wareyyeb, min xef tuɣa issawař unabi Daniyal, ittbedda mani war ittxeṣṣa ad ibedd - wenni iɣrin ad ifhem! - řexdenni ittxeṣṣa i yinni iǧan di Yahudiyya, ad arewřen ɣar idurar, \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt Dan. 9:27; Mt. 24:15; Lk. 21:20, 21. \x*
\v 15 u wenni iǧan x tzeqqa war dd-ihekkwi ca ɣar taddart u war ittidef ca ḥima ad iksi ca zi taddart nnes,
\v 16 u wenni iǧan deg iyyar war dd-ittɛiqqib ca ḥima ad iksi aseřham nnes.
\v 17 Uct x tinni iǧan s ddeyset d tinni issuṭuḍen deg wussan nni!
\v 18 Ẓaǧem ḥima war tᵉttiři tarewřa nwem di řmecta,
\v 19 Minzi deg wussan nni ad din tiři ict n řmeḥnet i war tuɣi am nettat zeg wami dd-ixřeq AREBBI ddunect ař řexxu, uca war tᵉttiři ɛemmarṣ ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Mt. 24:21\x*
\v 20 Mařa SIDI war issemẓi ussan nni, war tnejjem uřa d ict n ddat, maca di ṭṭweɛ n yinni ittwafarzen, inni i ixḍar Netta, aqa issemẓi ussan nni.
\m 
\v 21 Xenni mařa inna awem ijjen: ‘Aqa Lmasiḥ da!’, niɣ: ‘Aqa-t diha!’, war t ttamnem. \x ◘ \xo 13:21 \xt Mt. 24:23; Lk. 21:8. \x*
\v 22 Minzi ad kkaren imasiḥen ifalsuten d inabiyyen issxarriqen, ad ggen řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb ḥima, mařa izemmar, ad xedɛen ɛad inni ittwafarzen. \x ◘ \xo 13:22 \xt Aɛwd. 13:2; 2 Ts. 2:11. \x*
\v 23 Kenniw maca, ḥḍam, aqa marra nniɣ awem t qbeř.
\m 
\v 24 Maca deg wussan nni, awarni řmeḥnet nni, ad tebbarcen tfuct uca taziri war tᵉttic ɛad tafawt nnes, \x ◘ \xo 13:24 \xt Ica. 13:10; Ḥiz. 32:7; Yuw. 3:4; 3:15; Mt. 24:29; Lk. 21:25; Asa. 6:12. \x*
\v 25 itran ad dd-wḍan zeg ujenna uca ṣṣulaṭat i iǧan deg ijenwan ad ttwanhezzent. \x ◘ \xo 13:25 \xt Ica. 13:10; 34:4. \x*
\v 26 Xenni ad ẓaren Mmis n bnadem xmi dd ɣa yas deg iseynuten, s jjehd d uɛuǧi ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 13:26 \xt Dan. 7:10; Mt. 16:27; 24:30; Mk. 14:62; Lk. 21:27; Řex. 1:11; 1 Ts. 4:16; 2 Ts. 1:10; Asa. 1:7. \x*
\v 27 Řexdenni ad issekk lmalakat nnes uca ad iyru inni zzayes ittwafarzen zi arebɛa n tɣemmura n usemmiḍ, zi ṭṭarf aneggaru n temmurt ař ṭṭarf aneggaru n ujenna. \x ◘ \xo 13:27 \xt Aɛwd. 30:4, 5\x*
\m 
\v 28 Řemdem zeg wartu n tazart amettiř-a: xmi ɣa dewřen řefruɛ nnes ad dd-areḍben uca tifray ad dd-ffɣent, xenni ad tessnem aqa anebdu yiweḍ-dd. \x ◘ \xo 13:28 \xt Mt. 24:32; Lk. 21:29. \x*
\v 29 Ammu ittxeṣṣa uřa d kenniw, xmi ɣa tẓarem timesřayin-a ttemsarant, ad tessnem, aqa man aya yudes-dd, x tewwart.
\v 30 S tidett ad awem iniɣ, jjiř-a war iɛeddu ca ař d ɣa yiři man aya marra.
\v 31 Ajenna d temmurt ad ɛdun, \add maca\add* awařen inu war ɛeddun ɛemmarṣ. \x ◘ \xo 13:31 \xt Izhd. 102:27; Ica. 40:8; 51:6; Ɛbr. 1:11. \x*
\v 32 Maca ass nni d tsaɛɛet nni uřa d ijj war t issin, uřa d lmalakat nni iǧan deg ujenna, uřa d Mmis, mɣir Babas. \x ◘ \xo 13:32 \xt Mt. 24:36; Řex. 1:7. \x*
\m 
\v 33 \bd Xẓarem\bd*, ḥḍam, ẓaǧem, minzi war tessinem ca meřmi dd ɣa taweḍ řweqt nni. \x ◘ \xo 13:33 \xt Mt. 24:42; 25:13; Lk. 12:40; 21:36; 1 Ts. 5:6. \x*
\v 34 Aqa-t am yijj n bnadem ittxeṣṣa as ad isafar, ijja taddart nnes, iwekkeř imsexxaren nnes s ṣṣulṭa, iwca i kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* řxedmet nnes, uca iɛřem as i uɛessas n tewwart maḥend ad iqqim ad iḥḍa.
\v 35 Iwa ḥḍam xenni, minzi war tessinem ca meřmi i dd ɣa yas bab n taddart, ɣar uɛecci niɣ ɣar wezyen n ǧiřet niɣ ɣar usquqeɛ n uyaẓiḍ niɣ ɣar ṣṣbeḥ \add zic\add*,
\v 36 ḥima, mařa dd-ittis deɣya, war kenniw ittif tᵉtteṭṭṣem.
\v 37 Min d awem qqareɣ řexxu, qqareɣ t i marra: Faqem!”
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Udayen arezzun ad nɣen Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 1 Awarni i tnayen n wussan tuɣa teǧa \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu n \add Řɛid n Weɣrum\add* břa Antun, u tuɣa imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen arezzun ict n tewwart maḥend ad t ṭṭfen s teḥraymect uca ad t nɣen. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt [Mt. 26:1-5; Lk. 22:1-2; Yḥ. 11:45-53] — Mt. 26:2; Lk. 22:1; Yḥ. 11:55; 13:1. \x*
\v 2 Maca nitni nnan: “War ittiři di Řɛid, ḥima war ittiři uɣewwuɣ di řgens.”
\b
\s1 Adhan n Yasuɛ di Bayt-Ɛanya
\m 
\v 3 Řami tuɣa iqqim \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* di Bayt-Ɛanya di taddart n Cimɛun, wenni di iǧa řbarṣ, tusa-dd ict n temɣart, aqa-t ɣares ijj n uɣarraf n alabaster dayes zzect i wedhan zi řeɛṭur n ṣṣenbel teṣbeḥ, tiɣřa. Tarzem taziyyat nni, tfarreɣ i-tt x uzeǧif n Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt [Mt. 26:6-13; Yḥ. 12:1-8] \x*
\v 4 Tuɣa din ca n imeḥḍaren, xeyyqen aṭṭas deg ixef nsen x man aya, nnan: “Mayemmi aḍeyyeɛ n zzect-a i wedhan?
\v 5 Minzi iři ad tᵉttwammenz \add zzect-a\add* s ktar zi teřt-mya dinar uca xenni ad immewc i imezřaḍ.” Uca xeyyqen xas aṭṭas.
\v 6 Maca Yasuɛ inna: “Jjem tt! Mayemmi xas tᵉttɛeddam? Aqa tegga dayi ijj n cɣeř icna.
\v 7 Minzi imezřaḍ aqa aten řebda akidwem, tzemmarem ad kisen teggem řxar meřmi ma texsem, maca Necc war kidwem ttɣimiɣ řebda. \x ◘ \xo 14:7 \xt Aɛwd. 15:11. \x*
\v 8 Nettat tegga min umi tzemmar. Aqa tizzar temseḥ arrimet inu s řeɛṭur i wenḍeř.
\v 9 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ: Mani ma i ɣa ittwabarreḥ s Řexbar-a Aṣebḥan zzayi di marra ddunect, ad xebbaren ɛawed x min tegga, d řidaret i nettat.”
\b
\s1 Yahuda izzenz ixef nnes maḥend ad isellem Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* iruḥ Yahuda Isxariyuṭi, ijjen zi tenɛac, ɣar imeqqranen n ikehhanen ḥima ad asen isellem Yasuɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:10 \xt [Mt. 26:14-16; Lk. 22:3-6] — Mt. 26:14; Lk. 22:4. \x*
\v 11 Umi sřin man aya, farḥen uca waɛden ad as wcen \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart. U netta tuɣa yarezzu ict n tewwart, ḥima ad \add asen\add* t isellem.
\b
\s1 Asewjed n Amensi n Useɛdu
\m 
\v 12 Deg wass amezwar n \add Weɣrum\add* břa Antun, umi ttnuman Wudayen ad ɣarṣen i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu, nnan as imeḥḍaren nnes: “Mani texsed ad nraḥ ḥima ad nessewjed maḥend ad tecced \add amensi n\add* Useɛdu?” \x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt [Mt. 26:17-25; Lk. 22:7-14; 21-23; Yḥ. 13:21-30] — Uf. 12:17; Mt. 26:17; Lk. 22:7. \x*
\v 13 Issekk tnayen zeg imeḥḍaren nnes, inna asen: “Ruḥem ɣar tendint, u xzar, ad temsagarem ak-d ijj n weryaz, yarbu ict n teqbuct n waman. Ḍfarem t!
\v 14 U mani ɣa yadef, inim i bab n taddart: ‘Amseřmad nneɣ iqqar: Mani teǧa tɣurfet ḥima ad cceɣ \add amensi n\add* Useɛdu ak-d imeḥḍaren inu?’
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* netta ad awem immeř ijj n arwa imɣar sennej, issu, iɛdeř. Dinni i d aneɣ ɣa tesswejdem.”
\v 16 Ffɣen imeḥḍaren, usin-dd ɣar tendint uca ufin \add marra\add* am mammec tuɣa d asen inna, xenni sswejden i \add umensi n\add* Useɛdu.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Ɣar uɛecci yusa-dd ak-d tenɛac \add n rrusul\add* nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:17 \xt Mt. 26:20; Lk. 22:14. \x*
\v 18 Řami tuɣa qqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add*, ttᵉtten, inna Yasuɛ: “S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, aqa ijjen zzaywem wenni kidi ittᵉtten, ad ayi iɣdar!” \x ◘ \xo 14:18 \xt Izhd. 41:10; Řex. 1:17. \x*
\v 19 Bdan ttecḍinen, nnan as ijjen awarni wenneɣni: “Ma d necc?”
\v 20 Inna asen: “\add Aqa-t\add* d ijjen zi tenɛac i issisnen akidi aɣrum di ṭṭebṣi.
\v 21 Aqa Mmis n bnadem ad iraḥ mammec d as tura. Maca uct x weryaz nni zi ɣa ittwaɣdar Mmis n bnadem. Iḥřa as i weryaz nni mři war dd-ixřiq.”
\b
\s1 Amensi n Siditneɣ
\m 
\v 22 Řami tuɣa ttᵉtten, iksi Yasuɛ aɣrum, ibarek i-t, yarẓa i-t uca iwca asen t, inna: “Ksim, ccem, aqa ta d Arrimet inu.” \x ◘ \xo 14:22 \xt [Mt. 26:26-30; Lk. 22:15-20; 1 Kur. 11:23-25] — Irm. 16:7 \x*
\v 23 Xenni iksi řkas, iqada, ibarek, uca iwca asen t, u marra idsen swin zzayes.
\v 24 Inna asen: “Aqa ina d Idammen inu n Řɛahd n Jdid i ɣa ittwassizřen i waṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*. \x ◘ \xo 14:24 \xt Irm. 31:31; Mt. 26:28, Mk. 14:24, Lk. 22:20, 1 Kur. 11:25, 2 Kur. 3:6, Ɛbr. 8:6, 8, 13; 9:15; 12:24\x*
\v 25 S tidett, Necc ad awem iniɣ, Necc war sesseɣ ɛemmarṣ ɛad zi řɣiǧet n tzayart ař ass i di i tt ɣa sweɣ jdid di Tgeldit n AREBBI.”
\v 26 Awarni řami ɣennjen nitni iẓři n ttesbiḥ, ffɣen ɣar wedrar n Zzitun.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ izwar issiweř x wenkar n Buṭrus
\m 
\v 27 Inna asen Yasuɛ: “Aqa marra kenniw ad dayi tenderfem di ǧiřet-a, minzi tura:
\b
\m \qt ‘Aqa ad wteɣ Ameksaw\qt*
\m \qt uca ad ttwazuzzaren iḥuřiyyen.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:27 \xt [Mt. 26:31-35; Lk. 22:31-34; Yḥ. 13:36-38] — Zak. 13:7; Mt. 26:31; Yḥ. 16:32. \x*
\b
\m 
\v 28 Maca awarni řami ttwassnekkareɣ, ad awem izwareɣ ɣar Ljalil.” \x ◘ \xo 14:28 \xt Mt. 26:32; 28:10; Mk. 16:7. \x*
\m 
\v 29 Inna as Buṭrus: “Waxxa ad \add dayek\add* nderfen marra, necc war dayek ttnedrifeɣ ca.”
\v 30 Inna as Yasuɛ: “S tidett, Necc ad ac iniɣ, aqa ass-a di ǧiřet-a, qbeř i ɣa issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ tnayen n twařawin, ad ayi tenkared třata n twařawin.” \x ◘ \xo 14:30 \xt Mt. 26:34; Lk. 22:34; Yḥ. 13:38. \x*
\v 31 Maca netta tuɣa iqqar s tmijja ijehden ɛad aṭṭas: “Mařa ittxeṣṣa ad mmteɣ akidek, war Cek nekkareɣ, \add a\add* Sidi inu!” Uca am netta, ammu i nnan uřa d nitni marra. \x ◘ \xo 14:31 \xt Yḥ. 13:37. \x*
\b
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Yasuɛ di Xitsimaniy
\m 
\v 32 Usin-dd ɣar wemcan umi qqaren ‘Xitsimaniy’. Inna i imeḥḍaren nnes: “Qqimem da, ařami ẓuǧeɣ Necc” \x ◘ \xo 14:32 \xt [Mt. 26:36-46; Lk. 22:39-46] — Mt. 26:36; Lk. 22:39; Yḥ. 18:1. \x*
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* iksi akides Buṭrus d Yaɛqub d Yuḥanna uca ibda ittnexřaɛ, iggʷed aṭṭas.
\v 34 Inna asen: “Aqa řeɛmar inu icḍen ař řmewt. Qqimem da, teḥḍam!” \x ◘ \xo 14:34 \xt Yḥ. 12:27. \x*
\v 35 Yuyur cwayt ɣar zzat uca iwḍa ɣar temmurt, iẓẓuǧ ḥima, mařa iɛeddeř, ad xas teɛdu tsaɛɛet nni. \x ◘ \xo 14:35 \xt Mt. 26:39; Lk. 22:42\x*
\v 36 Inna: “Baba, Baba inu, kuřci tzemmared xas! Ksi xafi řkas-a, maca war ittiři min xseɣ Necc, maca min texsed Cek.” \x ◘ \xo 14:36 \xt Yḥ. 6:38. \x*
\m 
\v 37 Uca idweř-dd, yufa i-ten ṭṭṣen. Inna as i Buṭrus: “A Cimɛun, ma aqa cek tᵉtteṭṭṣed? Ma war tzemmared ad teḥḍid uřa d ict n tsaɛɛet? \x ◘ \xo 14:37 \xt Mt. 26:40; Lk. 22:45. \x*
\v 38 Ḥḍam, ẓaǧem, ḥima war tᵉttidfem deg ujarreb. Arruḥ aqa iwjed, maca ddat aqa teḍɛef.” \x ◘ \xo 14:38 \xt Gal. 5:17. \x*
\v 39 Uca yuyur ɛawed, iẓẓuǧ, iɛawed i wawařen nni d ijjen.
\m 
\v 40 Idweř-dd ɛawed, yusa-dd \add ɣarsen\add* twařa nneɣni yufa i-ten ṭṭṣen, maɣar tuɣa tiṭṭawin nsen deqřent u nitni war ssinen mammec xas dd ɣa yarren.
\v 41 Uca idweř-dd Netta ɣarsen twařa wiss třata, inna asen: “Ṭṭṣem řexxu, tareyyḥem! Aqa yudes-dd uneggar, tiweḍ-dd tsaɛɛet. Xzarem, Mmis n bnadem ad immewc deg ifassen n imednab.
\v 42 Kkarem, ad nraḥ. Xzarem, aqa da wenni d ayi ɣa isellmen, aqa yudes-dd.”
\b
\s1 Aḥebbes n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 43 Am tuɣa \add ɛad\add* issawař, yusa-dd Yahuda, ijjen zi tenɛac. Tuɣa akides iryazen aṭṭas s řesyuf d iɛumad. Usin-dd nitni zeg imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imseřmaden n idlisen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add*. \x ◘ \xo 14:43 \xt [Mt. 26:47-56; Lk. 22:47-53; Yḥ. 18:3-12] — Mt. 26:47; Lk. 22:47; Yḥ. 18:3. \x*
\v 44 Uca wenni t i ɣa iɣdaren tuɣa ittegg asen ict n řeɛřamet, iqqar: “Wenni i ɣa ssudmeɣ d wenni Netta. Ṭṭfem t uca awyem t-i-dd.”
\v 45 Deɣya yuyur ɣares, inna: “\add A\add* Amseřmad inu, \add a\add* Amseřmad inu!”, uca issudem i-t. \x ◘ \xo 14:45 \xt 2 Ṣm. 20:9. \x*
\v 46 Ssarsen xas ifassen uca ṭṭfen t.
\v 47 Ijjen zeg inni din ibedden ijbed ssif \add nnes\add*, iwta amsexxar n arrays n ikehhanen, iqess as amezzuɣ.
\v 48 Yarra-dd Yasuɛ, inna asen: “Ma axmi x yijj n uqṭaṭɛiy i teffɣem xafi s řesyuf d iɛumad, ḥima ad ayi tᵉṭṭfem?
\v 49 Kuř ass tuɣa ayi akidwem di Zzawect Tameqqrant sseřmadeɣ, war d ayi tᵉṭṭifem. Maca man aya imsar, ḥima ad ttwakemmřent Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 14:49 \xt Izhd. 22:7; 69:10; Lk. 24:25. \x*
\v 50 \add Xenni\add* jjin t imeḥḍaren nnes uca arewřen. \x ◘ \xo 14:50 \xt Ayub 19:13; Izhd. 88:9. \x*
\v 51 Iḍfar i-t ijj n uɛezri, tuɣa yarḍ ict n tecḍaḍt \add n řeqṭen waha\add* x tqeddit nnes, uca ṭṭfen t-i-dd.
\v 52 Maca netta ijja tacḍaḍt uca yarweř zzaysen d aɛaryan.
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ zzat i Jmaɛet Tameqqrant n Wudayen
\m 
\v 53 Iwyen Yasuɛ ɣar Qayafa, arrays n ikehhanen, uca munen-dd ɣares marra imeqqranen n ikehhanen d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imseřmaden n idlisen. \x ◘ \xo 14:53 \xt [Mt. 26:57-68; Lk. 22:54-55; 63-71; Yḥ. 18:13-14; 19-24] — Mt. 26:57; Lk. 22:54; Yḥ. 18:13, 24. \x*
\v 54 Tuɣa Cimɛun iḍfar i-t-i-dd zi řaggʷaj, ɣar daxeř n řemraḥ n arrays n ikehhanen, uca tuɣa iqqim jar iɛessasen, ittweqqaḥ ixef nnes ɣar tmessi.
\v 55 Tuɣa imeqqranen n ikehhanen d marra Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add* arezzun cchadet ḍidd i Yasuɛ ḥima ad t nɣen, maca war tt ufin, \f ◼ \fr 14:55 \fq ’Jmaɛet \bdit Tameqqrant\bdit*\ft - niɣ: ‘Jmaɛet n řḥukkam imeqqranen n Wudayen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 14:55 \xt Mt. 26:59; Řex. 6:13. \x*
\v 56 minzi aṭṭas tuɣa xas cehhden s ẓur, \add maca\add* cchadat nsen war ttmeřqint.
\m 
\v 57 \add Xenni\add* kkaren ca uca cehden xas s ẓur, nnan:
\v 58 “Neccin nesřa as umi inna: ‘Ad hedmeɣ Zzawect Tameqqrant i ittwaggen s ifassen uca di třata n wussan ad bniɣ icten nneɣnit i war ittwaggen s ifassen.’” \x ◘ \xo 14:58 \xt Mk. 15:29; Yḥ. 2:19. \x*
\v 59 \add Maca\add* uřa ammu war ttmeřqint ca cchadat nsen.
\m 
\v 60 Xenni ikkar arrays n ikehhanen di řwesṭ \add nsen\add* uca isseqsa Yasuɛ, inna \add as\add*: “Ma war dd-tarrid s ca? Min xak cehhden yina?” \x ◘ \xo 14:60 \xt Mt. 26:62. \x*
\v 61 Maca Netta isqar, war dd-yarri s ca. Isseqsa t arrays n ikehhanen ɛawed, inna as: “Ma Cek d Lmasiḥ, Mmis n Lmubarek?” \x ◘ \xo 14:61 \xt Ica. 53:7; Řex. 8:32. \x*
\v 62 Inna as Yasuɛ: “Aqa d NECC! U kenniw ad tẓarem Mmis n bnadem ittɣima x ufusi n jjehd, ad dd-yas s iseynuten n ujenna.” \x ◘ \xo 14:62 \xt Dan. 7:13; Izhd. 110:1; Mt. 16:27; 24:30; 25:31; Lk. 21:27; Řex. 1:11; 1 Ts. 4:16; 2 Ts. 1:10; Asa. 1:7. \x*
\v 63 Icarreg arrays n ikehhanen tcamir nnes, inna: “Mayemmi neḥdaj ɛad řechud!
\v 64 Aqa tesřim aceqqef \add nni\add*! Min dd awem iḍharen?” Uca marra ḥekmen xas belli isdaheǧ řmewt.
\v 65 Ca \add zzaysen\add* bdan ssusufen xas, ttřeḥḥafen i uɣembub nnes, ccaten t s řpuniyyat, qqaren as: “Nabb!” Uca wtin t iɛessasen x uqabsi nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:65 \xt Ayub 16:10; Ica. 50:6; Yḥ. 19:3. \x*
\b
\s1 Ankar n Buṭrus
\m 
\v 66 Řami tuɣa Cimɛun di řemraḥ swadday, tusa-dd \add din\add* icten zi tiyya n arrays n ikehhanen. \x ◘ \xo 14:66 \xt [Mt. 26:69-75; Lk. 22:56-62; Yḥ. 18:15-18; 25-27] — Mt. 26:58, 69; Lk. 22:55; Yḥ. 18:16, 17. \x*
\v 67 Umi t teẓra ittweqqaḥ, texzar dayes, tenna: “Aqa tuɣa cek ak-d Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri.”
\v 68 Maca netta inkar, inna: “War \add t\add* ssineɣ, war fhimeɣ min teqqared.” Iffeɣ barra ɣar tesqift n tewwart, uca řexdenni issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ.
\v 69 Umi t teẓra tayya ijj n umur nneɣni, tebda teqqar i yinni din ibedden: “Aqa wa d ijjen zzaysen!” \x ◘ \xo 14:69 \xt Mt. 26:71; Lk. 22:58; Yḥ. 18:25. \x*
\v 70 Maca netta inkar i umur nneɣni. Cwayt xenni nnan inni tuɣa din ibedden i Buṭrus: “S tidett, cek zzaysen nican, minzi cek ɛawed d Ajalili. Řḥarḍ nnec am wenni nsen.”
\v 71 Ibda ineɛɛeř ixef nnes, ittjjaǧa: “War ssineɣ Bnadem-a mixef tessawařem.”
\v 72 Řexdenni issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ wiss martayen. Ifekkar Cimɛun deg wawař i inna Yasuɛ: “Qbeř i ɣa issquqeɛ uyaẓiḍ wiss martayen, ad ayi tenkared třata n twařawin.” Xenni ibda ittru \add aṭṭas\add*. \x ◘ \xo 14:72 \xt Mt. 26:34, 75; Lk. 22:61; Yḥ. 13:38; 18:27. \x*
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Yasuɛ zzat i lwali Pilaṭus
\m 
\v 1 Deɣya ɣar ṣṣbeḥ zic mcawaren imeqqranen n ikehhanen ak-d imɣaren \add n řgens\add* d imseřmaden n idlisen d marra Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*. Nitni carfen Yasuɛ, iwyen t uca sellmen t i Pilaṭus. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt [Mt. 27:1-2; 11-14; Lk. 23:1-5; Yḥ. 18:28-38] — Izhd. 2:2; Mt. 27:1; Lk. 22:66; 23:1; Yḥ. 18:28; Řex. 3:13. \x*
\v 2 Isseqsa i-t Pilaṭus: “Ma Cek d Ajeǧid n Wudayen?” Yarra-dd xas, inna as: “Cek tennid \add t\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Mt. 27:11; Lk. 23:3; Yḥ. 18:33. \x*
\v 3 Tuɣa imeqqranen n ikehhanen ttcetcan zzayes zeg waṭṭas n tmesřayin.
\v 4 Isseqsa t Pilaṭus ɛawed, inna as: “Ma war dd-tᵉttarid s ca? Xzar, aṭṭas n yinni xak ittcetcan!” \x ◘ \xo 15:4 \xt Mt. 27:13; Yḥ. 19:10. \x*
\v 5 War dd-yarri Yasuɛ s walu, ařami itebhet Pilaṭus. \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Ica. 53:7\x*
\b
\s1 Yasuɛ d Bar-Abbas
\m 
\v 6 Innum iḍeǧeq i ijj n umeḥbus di kuř řɛid, wenni ixsen nitni. \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt [Mt. 27:15-31; Lk. 23:13-25; Yḥ. 18:39, 40; 19:1, 16] — Mt. 27:15; Lk. 23:17; Yḥ. 18:39. \x*
\v 7 Tuɣa din ijjen umi qqaren Bar-Abbas, ḥebbsen t ak-d imɣewwɣen, inni inɣin ijjen deg uɣewweɣ. \f ◼ \fr 15:7 \fk aɣewweɣ\ft - niɣ ‘řfawḍa’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:7 \xt Mt. 27:16; Lk. 23:19; Yḥ. 18:40. \x*
\v 8 Isɣuyy řɣaci uca nitni bdan ttᵉttarren zzayes ḥima ad igg am mammec tuɣa innum ittegg i nitni.
\v 9 Yarra-dd Pilaṭus, inna: “Ma texsem ad awem dd-arxuɣ i Ujeǧid n Wudayen?”
\v 10 Minzi tuɣa issen belli imeqqranen n ikehhanen aqa sellmen t zi řeḥsed.
\v 11 Maca imeqqranen n ikehhanen ɛarnen řɣaci, maḥend \add ad ttaren\add* ad asen dd-iḍřeq i Bar-Abbas. \x ◘ \xo 15:11 \xt Mt. 27:20; Lk. 23:18; Yḥ. 18:40; Řex. 3:14. \x*
\v 12 Pilaṭus inna asen: “Min texsem ad ggeɣ s wenni umi tᵉttřaɣam Ajeǧid n Wudayen?”
\v 13 Sɣuyyen ɛawed: “Ṣellb i-t!”
\v 14 Inna asen Pilaṭus: “Man tuɛeffna i igga?” Xenni arnin di tɣuyyit ɛad ktar: “Ṣellb i-t!”
\v 15 Am tuɣa ixs Pilaṭus ad issarḍa řɣaci, iḍřeq i Bar-Abbas, \add maca\add* isellem asen Yasuɛ, awarni řami t hettken s urekkuḍ, ḥima ad t ṣellben. \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Mt. 27:26; Yḥ. 19:1. \x*
\b
\s1 Iɛeskariyyen sseḥqaran Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 16 Gewwden t iɛeskariyyen ɣar daxeř n řemraḥ n Taddart n Ccraɛ, \add umi qqaren ‘Prituriyum’,\add* uca ssmunen marra řkumpaniyyet n řɛeskar. \x ◘ \xo 15:16 \xt Mt. 27:27; Yḥ. 19:2. \x*
\v 17 Ssyarḍen as \add ijj n werruḍ\add* d azeggʷaɣ, muden as ijj n ttaj s isennanen uca qqnen as-t,
\v 18 bdan ttseǧamen xas, qqaren as: “Azul xak, a Ajeǧid n Wudayen!”
\v 19 Tuɣa ccaten t ɣar uzeǧif s yijj n weɛmud n uɣanim, ssusufen xas uca uḍaren x ifadden nsen, ɛebden t.
\v 20 Awarni řami t sseḥqaren, kksen as aseřham azeggʷaɣ uca ssyarḍen as arruḍ nnes, xenni ssuffɣen t ḥima ad t ṣellben.
\b
\s1 Abrid ɣar ṣṣalib
\m 
\v 21 Ḥṣaren ijjen wenni dd-ikkin ssenni am dd-yusa zeg iyyar, Cimɛun zi Qayrawan, babas n Aliksandir d Rufus, ḥima ad as yarbu ṣṣalib. \f ◼ \fr 15:21 \fk zeg iyyar\ft - niɣ ‘zi řkampu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:21 \xt [Mt. 27:32-44; Lk. 23:26-39; Yḥ. 19:17-19] — Mt. 27:32; Lk. 23:26. \x*
\v 22 Iwyen \add Yeccu\add* ɣar wemcan \add umi qqaren\add* ‘Juljuta’, min ixs ad yini ‘Taceqquft’. \x ◘ \xo 15:22 \xt Mt. 27:33; Lk. 23:33; Yḥ. 19:17. \x*
\v 23 Wcin as binu ixeǧḍen s mirru \add d amarzag\add*, ḥima ad t isuw, maca Netta war ixs ad t isuw.
\v 24 Umi t ṣellben, bḍan arruḍ nnes, ggin xas akeccuḍ x min ɣa iksi kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:24 \xt Izhd. 22:19; Mt. 27:35; Lk. 23:34; Yḥ. 19:23. \x*
\v 25 Tuɣa tasaɛɛet d třata, \add aqa-tt d tesɛa n ṣṣbeḥ\add*, umi t ṣellben.
\v 26 Ssibbet n řmewt nnes aqa-tt di tira-ya \add sennej nnes\add*: ‘Wa d Ajeǧid n Wudayen’. \x ◘ \xo 15:26 \xt Mt. 27:37; Lk. 23:38; Yḥ. 19:19. \x*
\v 27 Ṣellben akides tnayen n ixewwanen, ijjen x ufusi nnes, wenneɣni x uzeřmaḍ nnes.
\v 28 Ammu i ttwakemmřent Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* i iqqaren: “Ittwaḥseb ak-d inni war iseggden.” \x ◘ \xo 15:28 \xt Ica. 53:12; Lk. 22:37. \x*
\m 
\v 29 Inni ssenni dd-ittekken, tuɣa ttceqqafen dayes, tthezzan izeǧifen nsen, nnan: “A Cek wenni i ɣa ihedmen Zzawect Tameqqrant uca ad tt tebnid \add ɛawed\add* di třata n wussan, \x ◘ \xo 15:29 \xt Izhd. 22:8; 69:21; 109:25; Mt. 27:39; Lk. 23:35; Yḥ. 2:19. \x*
\v 30 senjem Ixef nnec, hwa-dd zi ṣṣalib!”
\v 31 Ammu i t sseḥqaren ɛawed imeqqranen n ikehhanen ak-d imseřmaden n idlisen, nnan: “Tuɣa issenjem inneɣni, maca war izemmar ad issenjem Ixef nnes.
\v 32 Ejj Lmasiḥ, Ajeǧid n Israil, ad dd-ihwa řexxu zi ṣṣalib, ḥima ad nẓar uca ad dayes namen.” Uřa d yinni ittwaṣellben akides, kkwaren t.
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 33 Umi dd-tiweḍ tsaɛɛet setta, \add aqa-tt d ḍḍhur\add*, tewḍa-dd taǧest x temmurt marra ař tesɛa, \add aqa-tt d třata n uɛecci\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:33 \xt [Mt. 27:45-56; Lk. 23:44-49; Yḥ. 19:28-30] — Mt. 27:45; Lk. 23:44. \x*
\v 34 Di tsaɛɛet tesɛa isɣuy Yasuɛ s tmijja tejhed, inna: “Il, Il, lmana cabaqtani?”, min ixs ad yini: “\add A\add* AREBBI inu, \add a\add* AREBBI inu, mayemmi dayi tsemḥed?” \f ◼ \fr 15:34 \fk Il, Il, lmana cabaqtani\ft - tuɣa Yasuɛ issawař s yiřes n Třamit am t ssawařen marra Wudayen di Urcalim d temmurt n Ljalil.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:34 \xt Izhd. 22:2; Mt. 27:46. \x*
\m 
\v 35 Ca zeg inni \add din\add* ibedden, umi sřin aya, nnan: “Aqa Netta iřaɣa i Iliya!”
\v 36 Yuzzeř-dd ɣares ijjen, issuff ict n spunxa s řxeǧ, igga i-tt x uɣanim, iwca as ḥima ad isuw. Maca nitni nnan: “Raja! Ejj aneɣ ad nẓar ma ad dd-yas Iliya ḥima ad t-i-dd-issehwa.” \x ◘ \xo 15:36 \xt Izhd. 69:22; Yḥ. 19:29. \x*
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* isɣuy Yasuɛ s ict n tmijja tejhed uca isellem \add arruḥ nnes\add*.
\v 38 Ařeḥḥaf n wadaf ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant ittwacarreg x tnayen zi sennej ɣar swadday. \x ◘ \xo 15:38 \xt 2 Im. 3:14; Mt. 27:51; Lk. 23:45. \x*
\v 39 Umi iẓra řqebṭan n mya i \add din\add* ibedden zzates, isɣuyyu ammu s jjehd uca \add xenni\add* ibedd usuffeɣ n nnefs, inna: “S tidett tuɣa Bnadem-a d Mmis n AREBBI!” \x ◘ \xo 15:39 \xt Mt. 27:54; Lk. 23:47. \x*
\v 40 Tuɣa din ɛawed timɣarin xezzarent i-dd zi řaggʷaj, jar asent ɛawed Maryam n Majdala d Maryam, yemmas n Yaɛqub, amaẓuẓ, u n Yusis, d Salumi. \x ◘ \xo 15:40 \xt Mt. 27:56; Lk. 23:49. \x*
\v 41 tinni t-i-dd-iḍfaren, sexxarent xas umi t tuɣa di Ljalil. Tuɣa din uřa d aṭṭas n timɣarin nneɣnit tinni tuɣa akides i dd-igeɛɛden ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 15:41 \xt Lk. 8:2, 3. \x*
\b
\s1 Anḍeř n Yasuɛ
\m 
\v 42 Řami dd-tiweḍ tmeddit n Usewjed, \add tameddit\add* nni iǧan qbeř i ssebt, \x ◘ \xo 15:42 \xt [Mt. 27:57-61; Lk. 23:50-56; Yḥ. 19:38-42] — Mt. 27:57; Lk. 23:50; Yḥ. 19:38. \x*
\v 43 yusa-dd Yusuf zi Ramta, ijj n umcawar icennɛen n Jmaɛet \add Tameqqrant\add*, wenni tuɣa ittrajan Tageldit n AREBBI. Uca netta izɛem ad yadef ɣar Pilaṭus maḥend ad as ittar arrimet n Yasuɛ.
\v 44 Itebhet Pilaṭus umi immut ammu deɣya. Iřaɣa-dd i řqebṭan n mya, isseqsa t, ma immut qbeř řweqt. \x ◘ \xo 15:44 \xt Izhd. 34:22; Yḥ. 1(;31-38\x*
\v 45 Umi ifhem man aya \add zi řqebṭan n mya\add*, iwca arrimet i Yusuf.
\v 46 Isɣa Yusuf řecfen n řeqṭen \add azdad\add*, iksi t \add zi ṣṣalib\add*, icfen i-t \add di řecfen nni\add*, issars i-t deg wenḍeř i xebcen di sseǧaḥ uca isseqnunni ict n teṣḍart x tewwart n wenḍeř. \x ◘ \xo 15:46 \xt Mt. 12:40; 26:12; 27:60; Lk. 23:53. \x*
\v 47 Tuɣa Maryam n Majdala d Maryam, yemmas n Yusi, ẓrint mani t ssarsen.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Tanukra
\m 
\v 1 Umi iɛdu ssebt, tesɣa Maryam n Majdala d Maryam, \add yemmas\add* n Yaɛqub, d Salumi řeɛṭur ḥima ad t dehnent. \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt [Mt. 28:1-8; Lk. 24:1-12; Yḥ. 20:1-10] — Mt. 28:1; Lk. 24:1; Yḥ. 20:1. \x*
\v 2 Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ zic deg \add wass\add* amezwar n ssimana iwḍent-i-dd ɣar wenḍeř, ařami dd-tenqar tfuct.
\v 3 Nnant jar asent: “Wi d aneɣ i ɣa isseqnunnyen taṣḍart nni iǧan x wadaf n wenḍeř?”
\v 4 Řami xzarent, ẓrint aqa taṣḍart tᵉttwasseqnunni \add zeg wenḍeř\add*, waxxa tuɣa temɣar aṭṭas.
\v 5 Řami udfent ɣar \add yifři n\add* wenḍeř, ẓrint ijj n ubřiɣ iqqim ɣar uɣezdis afusi, yarḍ arruḍ d acemřař, uca nitenti nnxeřɛent. \x ◘ \xo 16:5 \xt Mt. 28:2; Yḥ. 20:12. \x*
\v 6 \add Maca\add* netta inna asent: “War ttnexřiɛent ca! Kennint tarezzunt x Yasuɛ Nnaṣiri wenni ittwaṣellben. Aqa Netta ikkar, war da iǧi, xzarent, aqa amcan mani t ssarsen. \x ◘ \xo 16:6 \xt Mt. 28:5; Lk. 24:5. \x*
\v 7 Maca ruḥent, inint i imeḥḍaren nnes uřa i Buṭrus, aqa ad awem izwar ɣar Ljalil. Dinni ad t tẓarem am mammec tuɣa i d awem inna.” \x ◘ \xo 16:7 \xt Mt. 26:32; 28:10; Mk. 14:28; Řex. 1:3; 13:31; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*
\v 8 Ffɣent \add deɣya\add* uca arewřent zeg wenḍeř, minzi tqebs i-tent tarjijit d ddehcan, uca war t nnint i ḥed, minzi tuɣa ggʷedent. \x ◘ \xo 16:8 \xt Mt. 28:8; Lk. 24:9; Yḥ. 20:18. \x*
\b
\s1 Aḍḥar n Yasuɛ awarni i tnukra nnes
\m 
\v 9 Ɣar ṣṣbeḥ zic deg \add wass\add* amezwar n ssimana ikkar-dd uca iḍhar-dd d amezwaru i Maryam n Majdala, tenni zi tuɣa issuffeɣ sebɛa n ccwaṭen. \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt [Mt. 28:9-10; Yḥ. 20:11-18; Lk. 24:13-35] — Lk. 8:2; Yḥ. 20:14, 16. \x*
\v 10 Tanita truḥ uca txebbar aya i yinni tuɣa akides iǧan, inni tuɣa iceḍnen u ttrun.
\v 11 Řami ina sřin belli Netta aqa iddar uca iban asent, war zzaysent uminen. \x ◘ \xo 16:11 \xt Mt. 28:\x*
\v 12 Awarni aya iban-dd s yijj n waddud nneɣni i tnayen zzaysen, umi tuɣa gguren nitni ɣar ijj n dcar. \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Lk. 24:13. \x*
\v 13 Uřa d ina ruḥen ɛawed uca xebbaren inneɣni, maca war uminen uřa d ina.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Ɣar uneggar iban-dd i ḥiṭac ařami tuɣa qqimen \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* uca iɛayar i-ten zi ssibbet n tikkest n l’iman nsen u zi ssibbet n řeqsaḥet n wuřawen nsen, minzi war uminen zeg inni t iẓrin awarni řami dd-ittwassnekkar Netta.
\b
\s1 Řumur ameqqran i ubarreḥ n Řexbar Aṣebḥan
\m 
\v 15 Inna asen: “Ruḥem ɣar ddunect marra, barrḥem s Řexbar Aṣebḥan di marra min dd-ittwaxeřqen. \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt [Mt. 28:16-20; Lk. 24:36-49; Yḥ. 20:19-23; Uf. 1:6-8] — Lk. 24:36; Yḥ. 15:16; 20:19; 1 Kur. 15:5. \x*
\v 16 Wenni yuminen u ittwasseɣḍeṣ, aqa iddar, maca wenni war yuminen, aqa ittwaḥaseb. \x ◘ \xo 16:16 \xt Yḥ. 3:18; 12:48. \x*
\v 17 Tina d řeɛřamat i ɣa iḍfaren inni yuminen: aqa nitni ad ssuffɣen ccwaṭen s Yisem inu, ad ssiwřen s iřsawen n jdid, \x ◘ \xo 16:17 \xt Lk. 10:17; Řex. 2:4; 5:16; 8:7; 10:46; 16:18; 19:6, 12. \x*
\v 18 ad ksin ifiɣran s ifassen nsen u mařa swin min ineqqen, war ten iḍḍarri ca man aya, uca ad ssarsen ifassen nsen x imehřac, ad ggenfan.” \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt Lk. 10:19; Řex. 28:5, 8. \x*
\b
\s1 Tameksit n Yasuɛ ɣar ujenna
\m 
\v 19 Awarni řami kidsen issiweř, immeksi Siditneɣ Yasuɛ ɣar ujenna uca issɣim Ixef nnes x ufusi n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 16:19 \xt [Lk. 24:50-53; Uf. 1:9-11] — Lk. 24:50, 51; Řex. 1:9. \x*
\v 20 Maca nitni ffɣen uca barrḥen di kuř amcan, u Siditneɣ tuɣa iɛawen i-ten uca issars řxeṭ nnes x wawařen nsen s řeɛřamat i yeggin. Amin.
\b
\m Aneggar n L’Injil Iqeddsen am mammec t ibarreḥ Markus. \x ◘ \xo 16:20 \xt Řex. 1:2; 14:3; 1 Tim. 3:16; Ɛbr. 2:4. \x* 
